[SPEAKER_00] postoji ta jedna, jedna, kako bi to rekao,

293
00:21:39,079 --> 00:21:41,019
[SPEAKER_00] mimetizam je možda stručnija riječ,

294
00:21:41,019 --> 00:21:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] oponašanje, loše oponašanje.

295
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:44,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ja već polazim od toga,

296
00:21:44,380 --> 00:21:45,819
[SPEAKER_00] ako nekog želiš oponašati

297
00:21:45,819 --> 00:21:47,839
[SPEAKER_00] ili ako već želiš biti dekadentan,

298
00:21:47,839 --> 00:21:49,720
[SPEAKER_00] onda radi to sa stilom.

299
00:21:49,720 --> 00:21:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] A ne da loše oponašaš s teškim akcentom,

300
00:21:52,000 --> 00:21:53,059
[SPEAKER_00] ne samo u otvorenom,

301
00:21:53,059 --> 00:21:55,200
[SPEAKER_00] nego i u prinesnom značenju, ako želite.

302
00:21:55,200 --> 00:21:57,339
[SPEAKER_01] Ko su loši oponašatelji u polackom dvrstvu?

303
00:21:57,339 --> 00:21:58,160
[SPEAKER_00] O loši oponašatelji se konkretno,

304
00:21:58,259 --> 00:21:59,660
[SPEAKER_00] gledajte naši političare.

305
00:21:59,660 --> 00:22:01,559
[SPEAKER_00] Tu ću možda napraviti jednu iznimku

306
00:22:01,559 --> 00:22:02,819
[SPEAKER_00] sa gospodinom Milanovićem.

307
00:22:02,819 --> 00:22:04,400
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam došao njega ovdje hvaliti.

308
00:22:04,400 --> 00:22:06,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ali dopada mi se kod njega

309
00:22:06,099 --> 00:22:09,299
[SPEAKER_00] što ne mijenja orkotave svog glasa,

310
00:22:09,299 --> 00:22:10,900
[SPEAKER_00] ima ravni glas,

311
00:22:10,900 --> 00:22:14,099
[SPEAKER_00] ima pogled oči u oči kad vas gleda.

312
00:22:14,099 --> 00:22:16,880
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo se davno i upoznali nekad kao diplomati.

313
00:22:16,880 --> 00:22:17,680
[SPEAKER_00] Bez ovdje...

314
00:22:17,680 --> 00:22:20,039
[SPEAKER_00] Pažete, nisam ovdje došao sad njegovu tu politiku ubranju.

315
00:22:20,039 --> 00:22:20,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ne morate.

316
00:22:20,619 --> 00:22:23,440
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, drago mi je to što ipak ima jedno stav.

317
00:22:23,440 --> 00:22:24,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ima stav.

318
00:22:24,180 --> 00:22:26,319
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, tu mi govori o njegovom karakteru.

319
00:22:26,319 --> 00:22:27,579
[SPEAKER_00] Veliki broj ljudi,

320
00:22:27,579 --> 00:22:28,980
[SPEAKER_00] bez ovdje su tu desni i ljevi.

321
00:22:28,980 --> 00:22:30,819
[SPEAKER_00] Gledajte, tu je opet...

322
00:22:30,819 --> 00:22:33,480
[SPEAKER_01] Mnogimu zamjeraju da pređe nekad granicu,

323
00:22:33,480 --> 00:22:34,420
[SPEAKER_01] da nije kulturan.

324
00:22:34,420 --> 00:22:35,380
[SPEAKER_01] Što vi kažete?

325
00:22:35,380 --> 00:22:36,759
[SPEAKER_00] No ne, to uopće ništa znači.

326
00:22:36,759 --> 00:22:37,859
[SPEAKER_00] Pazite, mi imamo isto,

327
00:22:37,859 --> 00:22:38,559
[SPEAKER_00] to je našalost,

328
00:22:38,559 --> 00:22:40,380
[SPEAKER_00] to sam primetio čak od vrlo pametnih

329
00:22:40,380 --> 00:22:41,319
[SPEAKER_00] i dragih Hrvata,

330
00:22:41,319 --> 00:22:44,160
[SPEAKER_00] da pate od jednog toga kompleksa Balkanštine.

331
00:22:44,700 --> 00:22:46,619
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerujte mi, ja ću me iz privatnih razvoja reći,

332
00:22:46,619 --> 00:22:48,259
[SPEAKER_00] možda zato ajte što sam isladao

333
00:22:48,259 --> 00:22:50,500
[SPEAKER_00] te njihove idiome i te jezike,

334
00:22:50,500 --> 00:22:52,359
[SPEAKER_00] pa nemam ni malo kompleksa da pače.

335
00:22:52,359 --> 00:22:56,019
[SPEAKER_00] Mogu se pohvala da često znam i njemcima i amerikancima

336
00:22:56,019 --> 00:22:59,160
[SPEAKER_00] njima komplekse za njihove felare.

337
00:22:59,160 --> 00:23:01,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam se možda tih Balkanezera

338
00:23:01,099 --> 00:23:02,740
[SPEAKER_00] možda više nagledao u Americi,

339
00:23:02,740 --> 00:23:05,460
[SPEAKER_00] čak i među tim njihovim diplomatskim elitama,

340
00:23:05,460 --> 00:23:07,660
[SPEAKER_00] a da ne kažem i u Njemačkoj, u Francijskom.

341
00:23:07,660 --> 00:23:09,779
[SPEAKER_00] A najgore mi je to ono što vas pogađa,

342
00:23:09,880 --> 00:23:12,059
[SPEAKER_00] što ljudi tu imaju jednu prevrtljivu stranu.

343
00:23:12,059 --> 00:23:14,240
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo čak i literaturu o tome.

344
00:23:14,240 --> 00:23:15,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ja nekad više volim čitati

345
00:23:15,480 --> 00:23:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ivano Brleć, Mažuranić ili braću Grim

346
00:23:17,539 --> 00:23:19,500
[SPEAKER_00] nego sve te političke traktate.

347
00:23:19,500 --> 00:23:21,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi vole glumiti.

348
00:23:21,059 --> 00:23:23,319
[SPEAKER_00] Naša politička klasa, ako gledate,

349
00:23:23,319 --> 00:23:24,799
[SPEAKER_00] to su loši glumci.

350
00:23:24,799 --> 00:23:26,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ja to vidim konačno ako gledate.

351
00:23:26,519 --> 00:23:29,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mislim samo na političku sadašnju,

352
00:23:29,039 --> 00:23:30,559
[SPEAKER_00] na vladajuću klasu.

353
00:23:30,559 --> 00:23:32,799
[SPEAKER_00] jer neću sad to Poplenkoviću

354
00:23:32,799 --> 00:23:35,599
[SPEAKER_00] ni njegovom kabinetu govoriti,

355
00:23:35,599 --> 00:23:37,859
[SPEAKER_00] nego općenito svi ti naši politički.

356
00:23:37,859 --> 00:23:40,839
[SPEAKER_00] Pa čak i ljudi koji bi mi ono potencijalno mogli bi drago.

357
00:23:40,839 --> 00:23:45,099
[SPEAKER_00] Dragi kao što su domovenski pokreti,

358
00:23:45,099 --> 00:23:46,380
[SPEAKER_00] suverenisti.

359
00:23:46,380 --> 00:23:48,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mogu reći individualno,

360
00:23:48,019 --> 00:23:49,980
[SPEAKER_00] cijeni mi njihovo Hrvatsko i sve ovo ono.

361
00:23:49,980 --> 00:23:52,359
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, uvijek sam malo skeptičan

362
00:23:52,359 --> 00:23:54,519
[SPEAKER_00] prema tom njihovom jednoj,

363
00:23:54,519 --> 00:23:56,119
[SPEAKER_00] ono što sam rekao mi mikro i mijenjenje,

364
00:23:56,119 --> 00:23:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] boje glasa.

365
00:23:57,640 --> 00:23:59,759
[SPEAKER_00] i konačno on novac radi svoje, svačatelja.

366
00:23:59,759 --> 00:24:02,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ja mislim, polazim u toga da niko ne bi smio

367
00:24:02,039 --> 00:24:04,819
[SPEAKER_00] više biti u četiri godine na Saborskoj klupi.

368
00:24:04,819 --> 00:24:05,539
[SPEAKER_00] Plus toga...

369
00:24:05,539 --> 00:24:06,940
[SPEAKER_01] Ma ima ih koji su od kad je...

370
00:24:06,940 --> 00:24:08,519
[SPEAKER_00] Od kad su tamo, da razumemo.

371
00:24:08,519 --> 00:24:09,700
[SPEAKER_00] I onda plus toga,

372
00:24:09,700 --> 00:24:11,920
[SPEAKER_00] kritičan sam prema svima tim desničarima,

373
00:24:11,920 --> 00:24:13,500
[SPEAKER_00] ali ako gledate malo njihov pedigre,

374
00:24:13,500 --> 00:24:15,640
[SPEAKER_00] svi su po par stranaka već promijenili.

375
00:24:15,640 --> 00:24:17,700
[SPEAKER_01] A dobro, imamo li mi uopće desnice u Hrvatskoj?

376
00:24:17,700 --> 00:24:18,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ma nemamo, ću te.

377
00:24:18,480 --> 00:24:20,380
[SPEAKER_00] Na žalost, u tome sam pisao često,

378
00:24:20,380 --> 00:24:22,240
[SPEAKER_00] to je karikatura, to nije desnica.

379
00:24:22,539 --> 00:24:23,859
[SPEAKER_00] A razloge znamo koje su.

380
00:24:23,859 --> 00:24:25,720
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo, imamo biološki razlog,

381
00:24:25,720 --> 00:24:26,720
[SPEAKER_00] a znate koji je.

382
00:24:26,720 --> 00:24:27,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ljudi umiru.

383
00:24:27,920 --> 00:24:28,960
[SPEAKER_00] A ne samo to.

384
00:24:28,960 --> 00:24:30,480
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo imali katastrofu, čujete.

385
00:24:30,480 --> 00:24:32,099
[SPEAKER_00] Znate što su kao u Karlovcu,

386
00:24:32,099 --> 00:24:33,980
[SPEAKER_00] tu kod vas desilo 45. godine.

387
00:24:33,980 --> 00:24:37,059
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko mladih, zgodnih, inteligentnih ljudi

388
00:24:37,059 --> 00:24:39,200
[SPEAKER_00] sa visokim kvotsetom inteligencije.

389
00:24:39,200 --> 00:24:41,579
[SPEAKER_00] I ne samo tu, nego u Šibeniku,

390
00:24:41,579 --> 00:24:43,039
[SPEAKER_00] a u Zagrebu, da ne kažem.

391
00:24:43,039 --> 00:24:47,559
[SPEAKER_00] Mi su koji izgubili ono najkvalitetnije ljude.

392
00:24:47,559 --> 00:24:48,839
[SPEAKER_00] To je bilo uopće klanje.

393
00:24:48,839 --> 00:24:50,619
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, biološki, ako gledamo genetsko...

394
00:24:50,619 --> 00:24:52,819
[SPEAKER_01] I danas desničar 21. stoljeća

395
00:24:52,819 --> 00:24:54,440
[SPEAKER_01] trebao izgledati, odnosno nastupati.

396
00:24:54,440 --> 00:25:00,019
[SPEAKER_01] I s čime bi trebao izlaziti van pred građane?

397
00:25:00,019 --> 00:25:01,500
[SPEAKER_00] Pa upravo što ste vi rekli,

398
00:25:01,500 --> 00:25:02,519
[SPEAKER_00] to je jedna pleonazma.

399
00:25:02,519 --> 00:25:03,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam koji je gramatika,

400
00:25:03,460 --> 00:25:04,539
[SPEAKER_00] kako hrvatski se izrazi.

401
00:25:04,539 --> 00:25:05,980
[SPEAKER_00] To kad kažeš desniče,

402
00:25:05,980 --> 00:25:07,500
[SPEAKER_00] to tako danas loše zvuči.

403
00:25:07,500 --> 00:25:09,359
[SPEAKER_00] Je li dosta to jedne, kak se to kaže,

404
00:25:09,359 --> 00:25:11,279
[SPEAKER_00] semantičke pojmovne...

405
00:25:11,279 --> 00:25:12,480
[SPEAKER_00] Da, svi misle opet...

406
00:25:12,480 --> 00:25:14,420
[SPEAKER_00] To su oni koji slušaju Tomsona,

407
00:25:14,420 --> 00:25:16,480
[SPEAKER_00] žele Antu Pavelića, tako da...

408
00:25:16,480 --> 00:25:19,140
[SPEAKER_00] Ante Paveli, koji samo pričaju Ave Marija

409
00:25:19,140 --> 00:25:21,039
[SPEAKER_00] i koji se klanjaju ima velikim dijelom.

410
00:25:21,039 --> 00:25:22,579
[SPEAKER_00] To je dovoljno svi jedan takvih nače,

411
00:25:22,579 --> 00:25:24,119
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam se takvih puno nagledao,

412
00:25:24,119 --> 00:25:27,279
[SPEAKER_00] da onda diskreditira cijelu tu jednu desni miso.

413
00:25:27,279 --> 00:25:29,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ponavljam, počnemo prvo

414
00:25:29,019 --> 00:25:30,799
[SPEAKER_00] od tog jednog biološke katastrofe.

415
00:25:30,799 --> 00:25:32,539
[SPEAKER_00] To je opća katastrofa dila.

416
00:25:32,539 --> 00:25:34,420
[SPEAKER_00] Možete i mene pitati slobodno

417
00:25:34,420 --> 00:25:35,960
[SPEAKER_00] šta se desilo s mojom familijom.

418
00:25:35,960 --> 00:25:37,660
[SPEAKER_00] Tata bio dva puta u zatvoru,

419
00:25:37,660 --> 00:25:38,579
[SPEAKER_00] sestra isto tak.

420
00:25:38,579 --> 00:25:39,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne znam opće kak sam živ

421
00:25:39,920 --> 00:25:41,500
[SPEAKER_00] i kak sam uspio sve to proživjeti.

422
00:25:41,500 --> 00:25:43,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, a je tu sve nekako desilo.

423
00:25:43,480 --> 00:25:45,240
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo malo ljudi u emigraciji

424
00:25:45,240 --> 00:25:46,819
[SPEAKER_00] koje sam upoznao,

425
00:25:46,819 --> 00:25:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] to je vrlo ba malo bilo.

426
00:25:48,000 --> 00:25:48,900
[SPEAKER_00] Sve je rastočeno.

427
00:25:48,900 --> 00:25:50,400
[SPEAKER_00] I nama smo možda,

428
00:25:50,400 --> 00:25:52,140
[SPEAKER_00] od baši famozni,

429
00:25:52,140 --> 00:25:53,019
[SPEAKER_00] kako se to kaže,

430
00:25:53,019 --> 00:25:56,220
[SPEAKER_00] unutarnji sekretarijat za unutarnje poslove

431
00:25:56,220 --> 00:25:57,819
[SPEAKER_00] ili republički ili federalni,

432
00:25:57,819 --> 00:25:59,700
[SPEAKER_00] kako su nazvali kad sam bio emigrant,

433
00:25:59,700 --> 00:26:01,279
[SPEAKER_00] oni su mene imali na liste,

434
00:26:01,319 --> 00:26:02,759
[SPEAKER_00] ali imali smo i mi njima liste.

435
00:26:02,759 --> 00:26:05,259
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ne bi sad išlo u to.

436
00:26:05,259 --> 00:26:06,839
[SPEAKER_00] Ako želite, možemo se to...

437
00:26:06,839 --> 00:26:08,440
[SPEAKER_01] Ajde, to ćemo nekom drugom prilikom.

438
00:26:08,440 --> 00:26:09,720
[SPEAKER_01] Imamo strašno puno tema.

439
00:26:09,720 --> 00:26:11,319
[SPEAKER_01] Da, pači, idemo mi na po rušima,

440
00:26:11,319 --> 00:26:12,420
[SPEAKER_00] ajmo Amerikancima lupiti.

441
00:26:12,420 --> 00:26:15,940
[SPEAKER_01] Ajmo mi lupati malo i po našim Hrvatima.

442
00:26:15,940 --> 00:26:17,500
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, izgubili smo davno pojam

443
00:26:17,500 --> 00:26:18,920
[SPEAKER_01] što je desničar, što je ljevičar.

444
00:26:18,920 --> 00:26:20,819
[SPEAKER_01] To ćemo se složiti.

445
00:26:20,819 --> 00:26:22,259
[SPEAKER_00] Ja, apsolutno, tu se složimo.

446
00:26:22,259 --> 00:26:23,500
[SPEAKER_00] Žao me je to reći,

447
00:26:23,500 --> 00:26:24,920
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi nisu uopće upoznati.

448
00:26:24,920 --> 00:26:26,339
[SPEAKER_00] I tu moram zamjeriti

449
00:26:26,339 --> 00:26:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] i našem kurikulumu.

450
00:26:29,000 --> 00:26:31,019
[SPEAKER_00] Svaka čast gospodinu Fuksu,

451
00:26:31,019 --> 00:26:32,640
[SPEAKER_00] svaka čast i gospodinu Obuljen.

452
00:26:32,640 --> 00:26:34,400
[SPEAKER_00] Možda on ima i svoje kvalitete,

453
00:26:34,400 --> 00:26:35,660
[SPEAKER_00] ali ja polazim od toga

454
00:26:35,660 --> 00:26:37,079
[SPEAKER_00] na kurikulumu moraju staviti

455
00:26:37,079 --> 00:26:38,920
[SPEAKER_00] ne samo autori koji su sada

456
00:26:38,920 --> 00:26:40,480
[SPEAKER_00] cool ili woke,

457
00:26:40,480 --> 00:26:42,019
[SPEAKER_00] ili politički korektni.

458
00:26:42,019 --> 00:26:43,400
[SPEAKER_00] Stavite i druge autore,

459
00:26:43,400 --> 00:26:45,119
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo u društvenim znanostima.

460
00:26:45,660 --> 00:26:47,420
[SPEAKER_01] Dajte kritičko razmišljenje.

461
00:26:47,420 --> 00:26:48,180
[SPEAKER_00] Kritičko razmišljenje.

462
00:26:48,180 --> 00:26:49,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ja o tome pišem

463
00:26:49,059 --> 00:26:50,079
[SPEAKER_00] i na mojim disertacijama

464
00:26:50,079 --> 00:26:50,880
[SPEAKER_00] što sam pisao.

465
00:26:50,880 --> 00:26:53,440
[SPEAKER_00] Masa mladih Hrvata

466
00:26:53,440 --> 00:26:54,839
[SPEAKER_00] opće nisu upoznati

467
00:26:54,839 --> 00:26:56,339
[SPEAKER_00] sa konzervativnom

468
00:26:56,339 --> 00:27:00,019
[SPEAKER_00] i revolucionarnom idejama

469
00:27:00,019 --> 00:27:01,779
[SPEAKER_00] iz Vajmarske republike,

470
00:27:01,779 --> 00:27:03,200
[SPEAKER_00] iz prvog stolja,

471
00:27:03,200 --> 00:27:04,640
[SPEAKER_00] iz Francuske,

472
00:27:04,640 --> 00:27:05,599
[SPEAKER_00] isto tako,

473
00:27:05,599 --> 00:27:06,740
[SPEAKER_00] što ima veze s fašizmom,

474
00:27:06,740 --> 00:27:07,339
[SPEAKER_00] da se razumemo.

475
00:27:07,339 --> 00:27:08,900
[SPEAKER_00] Bezobro što je veliki broj njih

476
00:27:08,900 --> 00:27:10,640
[SPEAKER_00] i polske iskrenuo o fašizam.

477
00:27:10,640 --> 00:27:12,319
[SPEAKER_00] Ali opće te ideje

478
00:27:12,319 --> 00:27:13,980
[SPEAKER_00] o njima nisu poznate.

479
00:27:15,039 --> 00:27:16,519
[SPEAKER_00] Onda nemamo pojma,

480
00:27:16,519 --> 00:27:18,160
[SPEAKER_00] nemaju niti o sociobiologiji.

481
00:27:18,160 --> 00:27:19,279
[SPEAKER_00] Pa sve u Americi

482
00:27:19,279 --> 00:27:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] nažalost zadnjih deset godina

483
00:27:21,000 --> 00:27:21,880
[SPEAKER_00] i to se ukinulo.

484
00:27:21,880 --> 00:27:23,480
[SPEAKER_00] U kojoj mjeri naši genij,

485
00:27:23,480 --> 00:27:24,640
[SPEAKER_00] naš hereditet utiče

486
00:27:24,640 --> 00:27:25,900
[SPEAKER_00] na moje ponašanje.

487
00:27:25,900 --> 00:27:26,180
[SPEAKER_00] Čujte?

488
00:27:26,180 --> 00:27:27,380
