[SPEAKER_00] jer pazite, postoji empiriski,

692
00:33:12,079 --> 00:33:13,440
[SPEAKER_00] forenzični, kako,

693
00:33:13,440 --> 00:33:15,519
[SPEAKER_00] genetski,

694
00:33:15,920 --> 00:33:17,859
[SPEAKER_00] markeri koji točno pokazuju

695
00:33:17,859 --> 00:33:20,660
[SPEAKER_00] činjenicu, ja, ne mogu sad ulaziti.

696
00:33:20,660 --> 00:33:23,559
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, postavite jedno banalno pitanje,

697
00:33:23,559 --> 00:33:24,500
[SPEAKER_00] najobičniji čovjek,

698
00:33:24,500 --> 00:33:26,460
[SPEAKER_00] ne treba biti čovjek neki intelektualac

699
00:33:26,460 --> 00:33:28,359
[SPEAKER_00] na televiziji,

700
00:33:28,359 --> 00:33:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] nek postavi pitanje koliko je

701
00:33:30,000 --> 00:33:31,720
[SPEAKER_00] Njemačka dala Nobelovca,

702
00:33:31,720 --> 00:33:33,799
[SPEAKER_00] a koliko je dala Etiopija Nobelovca.

703
00:33:33,799 --> 00:33:36,259
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto, recimo, u Americi ima

704
00:33:36,259 --> 00:33:38,660
[SPEAKER_00] manje više svi najbolji športaši,

705
00:33:38,980 --> 00:33:40,920
[SPEAKER_00] konkretno glede, glede odbojke

706
00:33:40,920 --> 00:33:44,019
[SPEAKER_00] i glede rukometa, su Afroamerikansi.

707
00:33:44,019 --> 00:33:46,640
[SPEAKER_00] Tu i tamo naćete, kao je Bijelca i kao je Hrvata.

708
00:33:46,640 --> 00:33:49,519
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, nećete naći rijetko kojega,

709
00:33:49,519 --> 00:33:51,920
[SPEAKER_00] ćete naći Afroamerikansa

710
00:33:51,920 --> 00:33:54,359
[SPEAKER_00] među markerima, odnosno koji sa snajperim

711
00:33:54,359 --> 00:33:55,440
[SPEAKER_00] znaju dobro rukovati.

712
00:33:55,440 --> 00:33:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] To su sve detalje.

713
00:33:57,000 --> 00:33:59,319
[SPEAKER_00] Pa evo, evo, banalna, glupa stvar.

714
00:33:59,319 --> 00:34:01,660
[SPEAKER_00] Idete sada, ako putujete avionom

715
00:34:01,660 --> 00:34:04,559
[SPEAKER_00] za Kuwait

716
00:34:04,559 --> 00:34:05,720
[SPEAKER_00] ili sa tim

717
00:34:05,720 --> 00:34:07,680
[SPEAKER_00] Iraqi Airways, šta ja znam,

718
00:34:07,680 --> 00:34:09,440
[SPEAKER_00] naluknite se malo u kabini

719
00:34:09,440 --> 00:34:10,639
[SPEAKER_00] koga ćete vidjeti tamo.

720
00:34:10,639 --> 00:34:13,360
[SPEAKER_00] Svaka čast. Ja cijenim Arapi, živio sam u Olžiru

721
00:34:13,360 --> 00:34:14,440
[SPEAKER_00] tri vodine, razumijete.

722
00:34:14,440 --> 00:34:17,219
[SPEAKER_00] Oni imaju kvalitete koje možda mi Hrvati nemaju.

723
00:34:17,219 --> 00:34:19,679
[SPEAKER_00] Jer nisam tu došao diskriminirati, da se razumijemo.

724
00:34:19,679 --> 00:34:21,460
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, žele da ljudi znaju

725
00:34:21,460 --> 00:34:24,059
[SPEAKER_00] ono što je ona latinska poslovica.

726
00:34:24,059 --> 00:34:25,059
[SPEAKER_00] Svakom svoje.

727
00:34:25,440 --> 00:34:28,920
[SPEAKER_00] Da svak mora imat svoje.

728
00:34:28,920 --> 00:34:30,019
[SPEAKER_00] A ne mogu biti sada

729
00:34:30,019 --> 00:34:32,960
[SPEAKER_00] neki maratonac, jer nemam za to kvalitete.

730
00:34:32,960 --> 00:34:34,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne mogu biti dobar

731
00:34:34,360 --> 00:34:36,099
[SPEAKER_00] autovuzač, jer nemam te dobre

732
00:34:36,099 --> 00:34:37,840
[SPEAKER_00] instinkte za to.

733
00:34:37,840 --> 00:34:39,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ali imam neke druge kvalitete.

734
00:34:39,619 --> 00:34:41,280
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, toga nećete.

735
00:34:41,280 --> 00:34:43,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam u Americi, doslovce prolazne ocjene

736
00:34:43,980 --> 00:34:45,639
[SPEAKER_00] morao davati svojim studentima

737
00:34:45,639 --> 00:34:47,820
[SPEAKER_00] kad se neke teške stvari išlo govoriti.

738
00:34:47,820 --> 00:34:49,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ali oni to nisu mogli shvatiti.

739
00:34:49,699 --> 00:34:51,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ja moram onda diplomatski se izraziti.

740
00:34:51,559 --> 00:34:54,300
[SPEAKER_01] A da ste od njih tražili ono što kako je

741
00:34:54,300 --> 00:34:55,880
[SPEAKER_01] trebalo onda biste opet bili na meti.

742
00:34:55,880 --> 00:34:56,840
[SPEAKER_00] Da se tražili onda bi...

743
00:34:56,840 --> 00:34:59,519
[SPEAKER_00] I to je, upravo se ta ideja egalitarizma,

744
00:34:59,519 --> 00:35:00,380
[SPEAKER_00] da smo svi jednaki.

745
00:35:00,380 --> 00:35:01,159
[SPEAKER_01] Jednaki, a nismo.

746
00:35:01,159 --> 00:35:02,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ne možemo biti.

747
00:35:02,059 --> 00:35:03,360
[SPEAKER_00] Pazite, kad meni neko kaže,

748
00:35:03,360 --> 00:35:04,500
[SPEAKER_00] ako mogu još jednu minutu...

749
00:35:04,500 --> 00:35:04,940
[SPEAKER_01] Svako ko?

750
00:35:04,940 --> 00:35:05,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ovako.

751
00:35:05,599 --> 00:35:08,039
[SPEAKER_00] Kad mi neko kaže, jesi si on prijatelj.

752
00:35:08,039 --> 00:35:09,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ja mogu biti prijatelj s jednim

753
00:35:09,500 --> 00:35:10,340
[SPEAKER_00] ili zvoje osve.

754
00:35:10,340 --> 00:35:12,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne mogu biti prijatelj sa sto prijatelja.

755
00:35:12,559 --> 00:35:14,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ili čovjek po prirodi diskriminira.

756
00:35:14,380 --> 00:35:15,639
[SPEAKER_00] Razumete?

757
00:35:15,639 --> 00:35:17,800
[SPEAKER_00] Ta riječ isto gadno zvuči.

758
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:19,480
[SPEAKER_00] Po prirodi ja pravim izbor.

759
00:35:19,800 --> 00:35:21,280
[SPEAKER_00] Otiđete u supermarketu,

760
00:35:21,280 --> 00:35:23,079
[SPEAKER_00] supernovu ili kako se već zove,

761
00:35:23,079 --> 00:35:25,699
[SPEAKER_00] pa gledam kavu koja mi više odgovara

762
00:35:25,699 --> 00:35:28,099
[SPEAKER_00] za moje bubrege, za kamence ili šta ja znam.

763
00:35:28,099 --> 00:35:28,860
[SPEAKER_00] Razumijete?

764
00:35:28,860 --> 00:35:30,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što meni odgovara.

765
00:35:30,300 --> 00:35:32,119
[SPEAKER_00] Isto, da budem, neću biti prost,

766
00:35:32,119 --> 00:35:35,099
[SPEAKER_00] nisam sad tu došao kao neki seksista govorit,

767
00:35:35,099 --> 00:35:37,659
[SPEAKER_00] pa čovjek kad ide sa ženom s nekom spavati,

768
00:35:37,659 --> 00:35:39,380
[SPEAKER_00] pa isto gledam da mi odgovara

769
00:35:39,380 --> 00:35:43,059
[SPEAKER_00] i po mozgu, i po svojoj fizijonomiji,

770
00:35:43,059 --> 00:35:45,599
[SPEAKER_00] i po, kako bih rekao, i konstituciji i tak dalje.

771
00:35:45,719 --> 00:35:48,840
[SPEAKER_00] Čovjek pravi uvijek, pravite diskriminaciju.

772
00:35:48,840 --> 00:35:50,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kad sam se ženio, gledao sam uvijek

773
00:35:50,960 --> 00:35:52,679
[SPEAKER_00] da mi je, o sreću, već sam 40 godina

774
00:35:52,679 --> 00:35:54,900
[SPEAKER_00] sa ženom za 50, razumijete?

775
00:35:54,900 --> 00:35:56,800
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, te ispravili ste se u rednije.

776
00:35:56,800 --> 00:36:00,159
[SPEAKER_00] I tu je, ja pravim uvijek izbore.

777
00:36:00,159 --> 00:36:01,699
[SPEAKER_00] Meni je, nekom je simpatičniji.

778
00:36:01,699 --> 00:36:04,559
[SPEAKER_01] Ali zašto mi danas ne smijemo više praviti izbore?

779
00:36:04,559 --> 00:36:06,460
[SPEAKER_01] U stvari možda ih možemo praviti,

780
00:36:06,460 --> 00:36:08,280
[SPEAKER_01] ali ne smijemo o tome govoriti javno.

781
00:36:08,280 --> 00:36:11,280
[SPEAKER_01] Pa mi se čini nekako da nam dolazi uskoro

782
00:36:11,280 --> 00:36:12,340
[SPEAKER_01] misalni delikt.

783
00:36:12,340 --> 00:36:12,860
[SPEAKER_00] Pa je pa to.

784
00:36:12,860 --> 00:36:15,059
[SPEAKER_01] Neka smo imali verbalni u uvijekšoj državi,

785
00:36:15,059 --> 00:36:17,159
[SPEAKER_01] ali sad misalni delikti imaju,

786
00:36:17,159 --> 00:36:19,119
[SPEAKER_00] njemci imaju krasari iza njemačke bogate,

787
00:36:19,119 --> 00:36:20,820
[SPEAKER_00] gezinungspolizei,

788
00:36:20,820 --> 00:36:22,539
[SPEAKER_00] znači misalna policija.

789
00:36:22,539 --> 00:36:24,820
[SPEAKER_00] To je ona iz Orwellove 84.

790
00:36:24,820 --> 00:36:27,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to nije gedanken, to nije thought police,

791
00:36:27,119 --> 00:36:28,960
[SPEAKER_00] to nije samo misalna policija.

792
00:36:28,960 --> 00:36:33,659
[SPEAKER_00] To je ona prije nego što si nešto zamislio.

793
00:36:33,659 --> 00:36:34,239
[SPEAKER_01] Prije nego što si pomislio.

794
00:36:34,239 --> 00:36:35,079
[SPEAKER_00] E tako je.

795
00:36:35,079 --> 00:36:37,039
[SPEAKER_00] To je prekrasna njemačka riječ.

796
00:36:37,039 --> 00:36:37,860
[SPEAKER_01] Čeka li nas to, profesor?

797
00:36:37,860 --> 00:36:38,039
[SPEAKER_01] Koga?

798
00:36:38,039 --> 00:36:39,420
[SPEAKER_01] Čeka li nas to?

799
00:36:39,420 --> 00:36:40,539
[SPEAKER_00] Pa čujte, gledajte,

800
00:36:40,539 --> 00:36:43,500
[SPEAKER_00] upet moramo se vratiti sve ovo što mi sad prolazimo,

801
00:36:43,500 --> 00:36:44,500
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam malo prije govorio,

802
00:36:44,500 --> 00:36:45,300
[SPEAKER_00] to je mimikriji,

803
00:36:45,300 --> 00:36:46,880
[SPEAKER_00] čak i kod naših političara,

804
00:36:46,880 --> 00:36:48,340
[SPEAKER_00] koji na lošem,

805
00:36:48,340 --> 00:36:49,840
[SPEAKER_00] ajde, ne samo na jeziku,

806
00:36:49,840 --> 00:36:50,360
[SPEAKER_00] na lošem,

807
00:36:50,360 --> 00:36:52,980
[SPEAKER_00] samo ponašaju stvari koje su već davno,

808
00:36:52,980 --> 00:36:53,880
[SPEAKER_00] mislim,

809
00:36:53,880 --> 00:36:55,699
[SPEAKER_00] koje su loše prošle,

810
00:36:55,699 --> 00:36:57,320
[SPEAKER_00] ne samo u Americi,

811
00:36:57,320 --> 00:36:58,139
[SPEAKER_00] nego i u Evropi.

812
00:36:58,139 --> 00:37:00,219
[SPEAKER_00] I evo me čuli da mi uvijek smo najgore

813
00:37:00,219 --> 00:37:01,639
[SPEAKER_00] pokupili iz komunizma

814
00:37:01,639 --> 00:37:04,179
[SPEAKER_00] i najgore sad pokupaljamo iz kapitalizma.

815
00:37:04,179 --> 00:37:05,820
[SPEAKER_00] Uključujući ovu temu

816
00:37:05,820 --> 00:37:07,079
[SPEAKER_00] koju smo malo prije načeli,

817
00:37:07,079 --> 00:37:09,800
[SPEAKER_00] dovoz stranih radnika,

818
00:37:09,800 --> 00:37:11,539
[SPEAKER_00] ja, oprostite,

819
00:37:11,539 --> 00:37:12,980
[SPEAKER_00] to moramo isto ne naglasiti,

820
00:37:12,980 --> 00:37:13,980
[SPEAKER_00] da ne dođe do zabune.

821
00:37:13,980 --> 00:37:16,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ja najmanje optužim,

822
00:37:16,019 --> 00:37:17,900
[SPEAKER_00] ja nimalo ne optužim te Nepalce,

823
00:37:17,900 --> 00:37:20,059
[SPEAKER_00] Pakistance, Afganistance,

824
00:37:20,059 --> 00:37:21,579
[SPEAKER_00] sutra ću vam doći iz Alžira,

825
00:37:21,579 --> 00:37:22,099
[SPEAKER_00] što je druga,

826
00:37:22,099 --> 00:37:23,139
[SPEAKER_00] ili iz Tunisa,

827
00:37:23,139 --> 00:37:24,219
[SPEAKER_00] to je druga paru kava,

828
00:37:24,219 --> 00:37:24,679
[SPEAKER_00] razumijete,

829
00:37:24,780 --> 00:37:25,820
[SPEAKER_00] njih je puna Francuska.

830
00:37:25,820 --> 00:37:28,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ja optužim ljude koji traže

831
00:37:28,059 --> 00:37:29,099
[SPEAKER_00] sitan profit,

832
00:37:29,099 --> 00:37:29,980
[SPEAKER_00] brzi profit,

833
00:37:29,980 --> 00:37:30,780
[SPEAKER_00] brze novce

834
00:37:30,780 --> 00:37:32,920
[SPEAKER_00] i nažalost neću sad spominjati imena.

835
00:37:32,920 --> 00:37:35,139
[SPEAKER_00] Čak i neka daljna moja rodmina,

836
00:37:35,139 --> 00:37:36,420
[SPEAKER_00] dole na obali,

837
00:37:36,420 --> 00:37:38,679
[SPEAKER_00] nije bitno gdje i na kojem otaku.

838
00:37:38,679 --> 00:37:41,139
[SPEAKER_01] Vidjela sam da vam je mama skrka.

839
00:37:41,139 --> 00:37:43,219
[SPEAKER_00] Je, sad ste pogodili.

840
00:37:43,219 --> 00:37:44,880
[SPEAKER_00] Pa isto ljudi koji isto,

841
00:37:44,880 --> 00:37:45,619
[SPEAKER_00] blobodurka,

842
00:37:45,619 --> 00:37:47,840
[SPEAKER_00] koji vole mahati s hrvatskim zastavama,

843
00:37:47,840 --> 00:37:49,340
[SPEAKER_00] koji vole hrvatovati,

844
00:37:49,340 --> 00:37:50,659
[SPEAKER_00] malo ću se narugati njima,

845
00:37:50,659 --> 00:37:52,659
[SPEAKER_00] ali koji tekako gledaju

846
00:37:53,860 --> 00:37:55,780
[SPEAKER_00] eventualno višak vrijednosti

847
00:37:55,780 --> 00:37:56,500
[SPEAKER_00] da se izrazimo,

848
00:37:56,500 --> 00:37:57,940
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno da strpaju sebi

849
00:37:57,940 --> 00:37:58,659
[SPEAKER_00] profit u žep.

850
00:37:58,659 --> 00:37:59,119
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

851
00:37:59,119 --> 00:37:59,880
[SPEAKER_01] hoćete reći,

852
00:37:59,880 --> 00:38:01,320
[SPEAKER_01] drže ruku na srcu

853
00:38:01,320 --> 00:38:02,139
[SPEAKER_01] dok svira imena

854
00:38:02,139 --> 00:38:05,500
[SPEAKER_01] i hvastaju se hrvastuma,

855
00:38:05,500 --> 00:38:05,920
[SPEAKER_01] u stvari,

856
00:38:05,920 --> 00:38:07,019
[SPEAKER_01] da tako kažem,

857
00:38:07,019 --> 00:38:08,400
[SPEAKER_01] dilaju s takvima.

858
00:38:08,679 --> 00:38:09,119
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

859
00:38:09,119 --> 00:38:10,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ili to im se više isplati,

860
00:38:10,639 --> 00:38:11,380
[SPEAKER_00] idu im na ruku,

861
00:38:11,380 --> 00:38:12,579
[SPEAKER_00] da ne kažem te agencije,

862
00:38:12,579 --> 00:38:14,019
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam što naša SOA radi

863
00:38:14,019 --> 00:38:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] i svi ti zakoni koji se tu šta tu...

864
00:38:16,000 --> 00:38:17,219
[SPEAKER_01] Da možda se bave vama.

865
00:38:17,219 --> 00:38:17,739
[SPEAKER_00] Vama.

866
00:38:17,739 --> 00:38:20,139
[SPEAKER_00] A čuti, ja vjerujem da je tamo možda ima ljudi koji prava.

867
00:38:20,139 --> 00:38:21,519
[SPEAKER_00] Čuti, čovjek je takav.

868
00:38:21,519 --> 00:38:23,739
[SPEAKER_00] Vrlo, ja sam onda sad malo ljudi upoznao.

869
00:38:23,739 --> 00:38:25,820
[SPEAKER_00] Da mu stvarno neko ponudi novac

870
00:38:25,820 --> 00:38:26,639
[SPEAKER_00] i da će onda odbiti.

871
00:38:26,639 --> 00:38:28,579
[SPEAKER_00] Malo prije sam mu uzao,

872
00:38:28,579 --> 00:38:29,380
[SPEAKER_00] reći ću sada,

873
00:38:29,380 --> 00:38:30,619
[SPEAKER_00] alegoriju sabora.

874
00:38:31,139 --> 00:38:32,880
[SPEAKER_00] ili to je isto životinsko carstvo,

875
00:38:32,880 --> 00:38:33,980
[SPEAKER_00] svoje vrste, razumijete.

876
00:38:33,980 --> 00:38:36,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ha, novac kvari su je.

877
00:38:36,019 --> 00:38:37,719
[SPEAKER_00] Čak i moje kolege koje vi isto dobro,

878
00:38:37,719 --> 00:38:38,719
[SPEAKER_00] ja jako dobro povezu,

879
00:38:38,719 --> 00:38:40,119
[SPEAKER_00] čak i visoko plasirani

880
00:38:40,119 --> 00:38:42,119
[SPEAKER_00] i u uredu i na jednom brijegu

881
00:38:42,119 --> 00:38:42,980
[SPEAKER_00] i na drugom brijegu.

882
00:38:42,980 --> 00:38:45,179
[SPEAKER_00] Ha, čujte, novac radi svoje, znate.

883
00:38:45,179 --> 00:38:48,980
[SPEAKER_00] Jedno je biti na penziji od 700 eura

884
00:38:48,980 --> 00:38:50,579
[SPEAKER_00] koje ja dobivam,

885
00:38:50,579 --> 00:38:52,840
[SPEAKER_00] da vam sad ne pričam i druge detalje,

886
00:38:52,840 --> 00:38:58,420
[SPEAKER_00] a drugo je imati plaću od možda 3000 eura

887
00:38:58,420 --> 00:38:59,579
[SPEAKER_00] mjesečno, razumijete.

888
00:38:59,699 --> 00:39:01,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ja svačam da to ljudima,

889
00:39:01,059 --> 00:39:03,239
[SPEAKER_00] ja znam, ja sam bio u toj napasti,

890
00:39:03,239 --> 00:39:04,159
[SPEAKER_00] ono što bi se reklo,

891
00:39:04,159 --> 00:39:06,800
[SPEAKER_00] tentacione, što je moja matara rekla,

892
00:39:06,800 --> 00:39:08,380
