1544
00:51:53,739 --> 00:51:55,440
[SPEAKER_00] mentalitet svoje drugove,

1545
00:51:55,440 --> 00:51:55,980
[SPEAKER_00] drugarice

1546
00:51:55,980 --> 00:51:56,579
[SPEAKER_00] sa Dedinja

1547
00:51:56,579 --> 00:51:57,380
