1548
00:51:57,380 --> 00:51:58,860
[SPEAKER_00] nego to sam to ja bio,

1549
00:51:59,000 --> 00:52:00,239
[SPEAKER_00] i zahvaljujući komunistima

1550
00:52:00,239 --> 00:52:01,320
