[SPEAKER_01] nekako to dobivaju,

1558
00:52:09,360 --> 00:52:10,119
[SPEAKER_01] rekla bih,

1559
00:52:10,119 --> 00:52:10,960
[SPEAKER_01] isto,

1560
00:52:10,960 --> 00:52:12,739
[SPEAKER_01] kroz genetiku,

1561
00:52:12,739 --> 00:52:14,119
[SPEAKER_01] da li se to nasljeđuje,

1562
00:52:14,119 --> 00:52:15,679
[SPEAKER_01] biti na vlasti u Hrvatskoj

1563
