1569
00:52:24,320 --> 00:52:26,719
[SPEAKER_00] ne pada jabuka daleko od drva.

1570
00:52:26,719 --> 00:52:28,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ja tekako to koristim,

1571
00:52:28,300 --> 00:52:29,119
[SPEAKER_00] prema da se razumiju,

1572
00:52:29,119 --> 00:52:30,820
[SPEAKER_00] u familijama imate svašta,

1573
00:52:30,820 --> 00:52:33,039
[SPEAKER_00] imate velikih tih razlika.

1574
00:52:33,039 --> 00:52:35,219
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, djeca nekadašnjih funkcionera,

1575
00:52:35,219 --> 00:52:36,219
[SPEAKER_01] kako se to zvalo,

1576
00:52:36,219 --> 00:52:38,320
[SPEAKER_01] su i dalje u tim istim vodama,

1577
00:52:38,320 --> 00:52:40,019
[SPEAKER_01] to se vidi i po prezimenima,

1578
00:52:40,019 --> 00:52:42,980
[SPEAKER_01] i ako je čovjek imao inteligentan zbroj 2 i 2.

1579
00:52:42,980 --> 00:52:44,340
[SPEAKER_00] Apsolutno, ja se tu s oma

1580
00:52:44,340 --> 00:52:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] apsolutno slažu.

1581
00:52:45,000 --> 00:52:46,500
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, nasljeđuje nas muči.

1582
00:52:46,500 --> 00:52:48,400
[SPEAKER_00] Nasljeđuje, to je tekako bitno,

1583
00:52:48,400 --> 00:52:49,500
[SPEAKER_00] ponavljam,

1584
00:52:49,500 --> 00:52:51,760
