1587
00:52:55,179 --> 00:52:56,199
[SPEAKER_00] da, tako već ne žele

1588
00:52:56,199 --> 00:52:58,099
[SPEAKER_00] vaši gledatelji čitati knjige,

1589
00:52:58,099 --> 00:52:59,559
[SPEAKER_00] nek barem počitaj bibliografiju,

1590
00:52:59,559 --> 00:53:00,820
