1596
00:53:07,360 --> 00:53:09,380
[SPEAKER_00] da sam toliko od moje mame naslijedio,

1597
00:53:09,380 --> 00:53:11,119
[SPEAKER_00] razumijete, tikove ili...

1598
00:53:11,119 --> 00:53:13,219
[SPEAKER_01] Možemo li se boriti s nasljeđem?

1599
00:53:13,219 --> 00:53:14,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ako vidimo da je negativno...

1600
00:53:14,699 --> 00:53:15,900
[SPEAKER_00] Nažalost, mi ne možemo,

1601
00:53:15,900 --> 00:53:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] živimo u multikulturalnom sistemu,

1602
00:53:17,539 --> 00:53:18,019
[SPEAKER_00] razumijete?

1603
00:53:18,019 --> 00:53:19,480
[SPEAKER_00] Jeste vi svjesnik opće,

1604
00:53:19,480 --> 00:53:20,219
[SPEAKER_00] opće je uropljena,

1605
00:53:20,219 --> 00:53:21,340
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno bijelaca ima.

1606
00:53:21,340 --> 00:53:23,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ima sve da 7% na svjetskom,

1607
00:53:23,199 --> 00:53:24,199
[SPEAKER_00] na kuglicem majskoj.

1608
00:53:24,199 --> 00:53:27,159
[SPEAKER_00] I u biti ta jedna konstrukt,

1609
00:53:27,159 --> 00:53:28,420
[SPEAKER_00] ili u biti tajan konstrukt

1610
00:53:28,420 --> 00:53:29,719
[SPEAKER_00] i liberalno komunizma,

1611
00:53:29,719 --> 00:53:31,039
[SPEAKER_00] ili komunizma i liberalizma

1612
00:53:31,039 --> 00:53:32,059
[SPEAKER_00] i multikulturalizma,

1613
00:53:32,059 --> 00:53:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] to je u biti jedna zamijenska ideologija

1614
00:53:34,000 --> 00:53:35,420
[SPEAKER_00] za taj komunizam,

1615
00:53:35,840 --> 00:53:37,079
[SPEAKER_00] polazi od pretpostavke,

1616
00:53:37,079 --> 00:53:38,860
[SPEAKER_00] daje ljudima samo dobru školu,

1617
00:53:38,860 --> 00:53:40,820
[SPEAKER_00] daje im dobre ekonomske mogućnosti

1618
00:53:40,820 --> 00:53:42,539
[SPEAKER_00] i ono što sam malo prije rekao,

1619
00:53:42,539 --> 00:53:43,539
[SPEAKER_00] stvorit ćeš od njih

1620
00:53:43,539 --> 00:53:46,579
[SPEAKER_00] kvalitetne i ljude,

1621
00:53:46,579 --> 00:53:47,659
[SPEAKER_00] bilo da karakterno,

1622
00:53:47,659 --> 00:53:49,039
[SPEAKER_00] bilo profesionalno,

1623
00:53:49,039 --> 00:53:50,119
[SPEAKER_00] što nije istina.

1624
00:53:50,119 --> 00:53:51,880
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ja znam da među tim ljudima,

1625
00:53:51,880 --> 00:53:53,420
[SPEAKER_00] među 6 milijuna a 5 milijuna

1626
00:53:53,420 --> 00:53:55,539
[SPEAKER_00] latinoamerikanaca,

1627
00:53:55,539 --> 00:53:56,679
[SPEAKER_00] pretežno mulatosa,

1628
00:53:56,679 --> 00:53:58,360
[SPEAKER_00] koje su došle iz Latinske Amerike,

1629
