[SPEAKER_00] ali ima i kriminalaca,

1634
00:54:06,840 --> 00:54:07,619
[SPEAKER_00] koji je urođeno,

1635
00:54:07,619 --> 00:54:08,980
[SPEAKER_00] da budu kriminalci,

1636
00:54:08,980 --> 00:54:09,300
[SPEAKER_00] znate,

1637
00:54:09,300 --> 00:54:10,460
[SPEAKER_00] i to ne smije,

1638
00:54:10,460 --> 00:54:10,900
[SPEAKER_00] ma mislim,

1639
00:54:10,900 --> 00:54:11,280
[SPEAKER_00] pasite,

1640
00:54:11,280 --> 00:54:12,099
[SPEAKER_00] dovoljno da...

1641
00:54:12,099 --> 00:54:13,239
[SPEAKER_01] Ne smije se na to zatvarati oče.

1642
00:54:13,239 --> 00:54:15,239
[SPEAKER_00] Da li se upanavljam,

1643
00:54:15,239 --> 00:54:16,059
[SPEAKER_00] reči vam otvoreno.

1644
00:54:16,059 --> 00:54:18,019
[SPEAKER_00] Mi se sad stavno vadimo

1645
00:54:18,019 --> 00:54:19,639
[SPEAKER_00] na taj famazni turizam,

1646
00:54:19,639 --> 00:54:21,139
[SPEAKER_00] pitanje kakav će turizam biti.

1647
00:54:21,139 --> 00:54:22,500
[SPEAKER_00] Uzmite moju riječ,

1648
00:54:22,500 --> 00:54:23,980
[SPEAKER_00] pa zanimam me ako se nađemo

1649
00:54:23,980 --> 00:54:24,760
[SPEAKER_00] za dvije godine.

1650
00:54:24,760 --> 00:54:26,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se nada mi prije,

1651
