[SPEAKER_01] ali dobro, ok.

1652
00:54:27,039 --> 00:54:28,400
[SPEAKER_00] Da, za dvije godine

1653
00:54:28,400 --> 00:54:29,079
[SPEAKER_00] ako se nađemo

1654
00:54:29,079 --> 00:54:30,079
[SPEAKER_00] baš trećeg velječna

1655
00:54:30,079 --> 00:54:30,760
[SPEAKER_00] svetov vlaho.

1656
00:54:30,760 --> 00:54:31,960
[SPEAKER_00] Meni je drugo ime i vlaho,

1657
00:54:31,960 --> 00:54:32,360
[SPEAKER_00] Blaž,

1658
00:54:32,360 --> 00:54:33,460
[SPEAKER_00] jer mi je Čača,

1659
00:54:33,460 --> 00:54:34,159
