1662
00:54:37,360 --> 00:54:38,400
[SPEAKER_00] ne da ja to prizivam,

1663
00:54:38,400 --> 00:54:40,500
[SPEAKER_00] da ovo ljeto pred svetim vlahom

1664
00:54:40,500 --> 00:54:41,519
[SPEAKER_00] pukne jedna petarda

1665
00:54:41,519 --> 00:54:44,519
[SPEAKER_00] i da tamo bude grupa tih

1666
00:54:44,519 --> 00:54:46,599
[SPEAKER_00] Nepalaca ili Pakistanaca.

1667
00:54:46,599 --> 00:54:48,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ode vam tu turizna do Djavova.

1668
00:54:48,599 --> 00:54:49,320
[SPEAKER_00] Nema još.

1669
00:54:49,320 --> 00:54:50,699
[SPEAKER_01] I gdje smo?

1670
00:54:50,699 --> 00:54:51,079
[SPEAKER_01] Nigdje.

1671
00:54:51,079 --> 00:54:51,619
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, nigdje.

1672
00:54:51,619 --> 00:54:53,280
[SPEAKER_00] Onda ćemo ići vratice na zemlju,

1673
00:54:53,280 --> 00:54:54,300
[SPEAKER_00] ići malo kopati

1674
00:54:54,300 --> 00:54:56,800
[SPEAKER_00] i pjevati po Dučkom kućici Bele.

1675
00:54:56,800 --> 00:54:58,239
[SPEAKER_01] Da, drago žerbe.

1676
00:54:58,239 --> 00:55:01,659
[SPEAKER_01] Kad smo već opet malo u Hrvatskoj,

1677
00:55:01,659 --> 00:55:03,119
[SPEAKER_01] rekli ste da ne očekujete

1678
00:55:03,119 --> 00:55:05,739
[SPEAKER_01] nekakve promjene od parlamentarnih izbora,

1679
00:55:05,739 --> 00:55:07,340
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno nakon parlamentarnih izbora.

1680
00:55:07,340 --> 00:55:09,119
[SPEAKER_01] A gdje je onda budućnost Hrvatske?

1681
00:55:09,119 --> 00:55:10,579
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, zvuči depresivno

1682
00:55:10,579 --> 00:55:12,300
[SPEAKER_01] i sad se vraćamo na onu depresiju vašu.

1683
00:55:12,300 --> 00:55:14,280
[SPEAKER_01] Jeste li izbog toga,

1684
00:55:14,280 --> 00:55:15,980
[SPEAKER_01] zbog toga što možda vidite

1685
00:55:15,980 --> 00:55:18,079
[SPEAKER_01] na drugačiji način nego ostali ljudi,

1686
00:55:18,079 --> 00:55:19,579
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je budućnost Hrvatske?

1687
00:55:19,579 --> 00:55:20,940
[SPEAKER_01] Jeste li izbog toga depresivni?

1688
00:55:21,179 --> 00:55:23,039
[SPEAKER_00] Pa to je, povesti, moj idealizam.

1689
00:55:23,039 --> 00:55:24,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam da li je to bila moja glupost

1690
00:55:24,599 --> 00:55:25,380
[SPEAKER_00] ili naivnost.

1691
00:55:25,380 --> 00:55:27,480
[SPEAKER_00] Tako sam odgajan opet genetski.

1692
00:55:27,480 --> 00:55:29,199
[SPEAKER_00] Taka mi je Čača bio predpostavljam.

1693
00:55:29,199 --> 00:55:30,739
[SPEAKER_00] Moja mater je isto,

1694
00:55:30,739 --> 00:55:32,420
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne znam,

1695
00:55:32,420 --> 00:55:33,980
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek predpostavljam od predpostavke

1696
00:55:33,980 --> 00:55:35,079
[SPEAKER_00] da zajednica,

1697
00:55:35,079 --> 00:55:36,300
[SPEAKER_00] kako god je zvali,

1698
00:55:36,300 --> 00:55:37,559
[SPEAKER_00] da li je to Hrvatska zajednica,

1699
00:55:37,559 --> 00:55:39,360
[SPEAKER_00] prem da se bojim i te riječi,

1700
00:55:39,360 --> 00:55:41,519
[SPEAKER_00] jer se danas previše Hrvatovije znate,

1701
00:55:41,519 --> 00:55:44,599
[SPEAKER_00] ali da uvijek moram stavljati

1702
00:55:44,599 --> 00:55:46,559
[SPEAKER_00] interese zajednice i društva

1703
00:55:46,559 --> 00:55:48,420
[SPEAKER_00] iznad svojih privatnih interesa.

1704
00:55:48,559 --> 00:55:49,579
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, to ne vidim.

1705
00:55:49,579 --> 00:55:50,480
[SPEAKER_00] To se gubi.

1706
00:55:50,480 --> 00:55:52,559
[SPEAKER_00] Upravo iz razlova koje sam nadeo,

1707
00:55:52,559 --> 00:55:53,320
[SPEAKER_00] tih genetskih,

1708
00:55:53,320 --> 00:55:55,739
[SPEAKER_00] a onda i ovo što prego razne,

1709
00:55:55,739 --> 00:55:56,639
[SPEAKER_00] razne tih filmova,

1710
00:55:56,639 --> 00:55:57,900
[SPEAKER_00] bilo iz Hollywooda,

1711
00:55:57,900 --> 00:55:59,719
[SPEAKER_00] ih tih sapunica dobivam.

1712
00:55:59,719 --> 00:56:01,420
[SPEAKER_00] Čak paradoksalno ispadali

1713
00:56:01,420 --> 00:56:03,579
[SPEAKER_00] u ove turske sapunice puno normalnije

1714
00:56:03,579 --> 00:56:04,960
[SPEAKER_00] nego ove što dobivam iz Hollywooda.

1715
00:56:04,960 --> 00:56:05,800
[SPEAKER_01] Što mislite o njima?

1716
00:56:05,800 --> 00:56:07,360
[SPEAKER_01] Neki kažu da je to njihov zapravo

1717
00:56:07,360 --> 00:56:09,980
[SPEAKER_01] onako perfidni ulaz kulturom.

1718
00:56:09,980 --> 00:56:12,019
[SPEAKER_00] Pa je, u svakkoj jedna kulturna politika.

1719
00:56:12,019 --> 00:56:13,380
[SPEAKER_00] Izvareno rade, čujte.

1720
00:56:13,380 --> 00:56:15,840
[SPEAKER_00] Nemamo zaboraviti kakva je turska kulturna.

1721
00:56:15,840 --> 00:56:17,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam bio tamo dva puta

1722
00:56:17,380 --> 00:56:18,960
[SPEAKER_00] isto na nekim njihovim programima.

1723
00:56:18,960 --> 00:56:22,099
[SPEAKER_00] Čujte, već kad smo ko te rasne strane.

1724
00:56:22,099 --> 00:56:25,260
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su i tekako ponosni

1725
00:56:25,260 --> 00:56:26,860
[SPEAKER_00] turski diplomati

1726
00:56:26,860 --> 00:56:28,539
[SPEAKER_00] kad kažu da su

1727
00:56:28,539 --> 00:56:30,739
[SPEAKER_00] albanskog, kosovskog

1728
00:56:30,739 --> 00:56:32,519
[SPEAKER_00] ili bosanskog podrijetla.

1729
00:56:32,519 --> 00:56:34,099
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, druge rečenje, kad kažu

1730
00:56:34,099 --> 00:56:35,500
[SPEAKER_00] na svoje evropsko podrijetlo,

1731
00:56:35,500 --> 00:56:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] baš ne vole svoje turkmensko podrijetlo

1732
00:56:38,000 --> 00:56:38,679
[SPEAKER_00] i stica.

1733
00:56:38,679 --> 00:56:40,119
[SPEAKER_00] To mi isto tako je u Meksiku.

1734
00:56:40,119 --> 00:56:42,320
[SPEAKER_00] Cijela njihova diplomacija, manje više,

1735
00:56:42,320 --> 00:56:44,239
[SPEAKER_00] to nisu mu latos i mesticosi.

1736
00:56:44,239 --> 00:56:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] To su praktički sve bijelci

1737
00:56:46,000 --> 00:56:48,519
[SPEAKER_00] španjalskog, čisto španjalskog podrijetla.

1738
00:56:48,519 --> 00:56:51,099
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, koliko god mi želimo potpuno tu rasu

1739
00:56:51,099 --> 00:56:53,059
[SPEAKER_00] izbaciti van svak od nas

1740
00:56:53,059 --> 00:56:55,099
[SPEAKER_00] podsvjesno zna vrlo, vrlo dobro

1741
00:56:55,099 --> 00:56:56,539
[SPEAKER_00] kojem plemenu pripada.

1742
00:56:56,539 --> 00:56:59,219
[SPEAKER_01] Gdje su onda tu u tom svijetlu

1743
00:56:59,219 --> 00:57:00,199
[SPEAKER_01] primjerice Mađari?

1744
00:57:00,199 --> 00:57:01,019
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto vas to pitam?

1745
00:57:01,019 --> 00:57:02,300
[SPEAKER_01] Zbog korbana njihovog,

1746
00:57:02,300 --> 00:57:04,960
[SPEAKER_01] koji se postavlja kao nekakavajde,

1747
00:57:04,960 --> 00:57:06,800
[SPEAKER_01] onako dečku koji muti planove

1748
00:57:06,800 --> 00:57:08,599
[SPEAKER_01] Evropskoj uniji,

1749
00:57:08,599 --> 00:57:10,880
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda Đorđa Meloni ga malo primiri.

1750
00:57:10,880 --> 00:57:12,460
[SPEAKER_01] Što je tu s Mađarima?

1751
00:57:12,460 --> 00:57:13,599
[SPEAKER_01] Gdje su oni po vama?

1752
00:57:13,599 --> 00:57:15,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ja u svom slučaju cijenim što vam radimo

1753
00:57:15,980 --> 00:57:17,280
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo pametnu politiku.

1754
00:57:17,280 --> 00:57:18,880
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo potrebamo se skinuti kapa,

1755
00:57:18,960 --> 00:57:20,420
[SPEAKER_00] ili je bio on rijetkih troje njih.

1756
00:57:20,420 --> 00:57:22,219
[SPEAKER_00] Svomu je Demirelo,

1757
00:57:22,219 --> 00:57:22,980
[SPEAKER_00] ako se ne odvaram,

1758
00:57:22,980 --> 00:57:24,880
[SPEAKER_00] on je jedini bio na Tuđmanovom sprovodu.

1759
00:57:24,880 --> 00:57:26,599
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam došao do sad hvali Tuđmana,

1760
00:57:26,599 --> 00:57:27,320
[SPEAKER_00] ali daje mu je on.

1761
00:57:27,320 --> 00:57:28,960
[SPEAKER_01] Treba na to pocijetiti.

1762
00:57:28,960 --> 00:57:30,159
[SPEAKER_00] Treba i na njegove radove.

1763
00:57:30,159 --> 00:57:31,519
[SPEAKER_00] On je bio je tu savršen čovjek,

1764
00:57:31,519 --> 00:57:32,960
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo u svojoj historiografi.

1765
00:57:33,599 --> 00:57:35,380
[SPEAKER_00] Gledajte, on je ipak došao,

1766
00:57:35,380 --> 00:57:36,739
[SPEAKER_00] jer je da još je mlad bio,

1767
00:57:36,739 --> 00:57:39,760
[SPEAKER_00] prije 20 godine već prošlo.

1768
00:57:39,760 --> 00:57:41,719
[SPEAKER_00] 30, ne znam, 20 i nešto.

1769
00:57:41,719 --> 00:57:43,780
[SPEAKER_00] Tu mu se treba skinuti kapa.

1770
00:57:43,780 --> 00:57:46,679
[SPEAKER_00] Drugo, on je ipak svjestan položaja Mađarskega,

1771
00:57:46,679 --> 00:57:48,619
[SPEAKER_00] na vrlo, vrlo jednoj delikatnoj poziciji,

1772
00:57:48,619 --> 00:57:49,880
[SPEAKER_00] to je kontinentalna zemlja.

1773
00:57:49,880 --> 00:57:52,820
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su nekad imali izlaz na more,

1774
00:57:52,820 --> 00:57:54,280
[SPEAKER_00] imali su admirala Hortija,

1775
00:57:54,679 --> 00:57:58,719
[SPEAKER_00] ili je loa rijeka i bila njihov izlaz na more.

1776
00:57:58,719 --> 00:58:00,139
[SPEAKER_00] Ali sve do svemo,

1777
00:58:00,139 --> 00:58:02,480
[SPEAKER_00] vjerujem da drži jednu dobru politiku,

1778
00:58:02,480 --> 00:58:04,079
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo umjerinu ideje.

1779
00:58:04,079 --> 00:58:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, ja on je jedan dosta ustran čovjek,

1780
00:58:06,000 --> 00:58:07,500
[SPEAKER_00] nije prost, nije divljak,

1781
00:58:07,500 --> 00:58:10,179
[SPEAKER_00] ali realan je.

1782
00:58:10,179 --> 00:58:13,460
[SPEAKER_00] Gledam, mislim, kakve su mogućnosti

1783
00:58:13,460 --> 00:58:15,219
[SPEAKER_00] i kakve su moguće konsekvence.

1784
00:58:15,219 --> 00:58:18,619
[SPEAKER_00] To je jedan tsunami tih migranata.

1785
00:58:18,619 --> 00:58:20,880
[SPEAKER_00] Nije to sad samo tako preko noće.

1786
00:58:20,880 --> 00:58:22,699
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, imam pozitivno mišljenje o njemu.

1787
00:58:22,699 --> 00:58:25,320
[SPEAKER_00] I drago mi je isto, bez odvrza što on dobio ordenje

1788
00:58:25,320 --> 00:58:29,699
[SPEAKER_00] i od Republike Srpske u Bosni,

1789
00:58:29,699 --> 00:58:30,559
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno od Odika,

1790
00:58:30,559 --> 00:58:32,639
[SPEAKER_00] dobio ordenje od Istovučića,

1791
00:58:32,639 --> 00:58:34,659
[SPEAKER_00] ali igra jednu pametnu politiku,

1792
00:58:34,659 --> 00:58:35,960
[SPEAKER_00] voli i Hrvate,

1793
00:58:35,960 --> 00:58:37,539
[SPEAKER_00] ali isto tako je svjestani

1794
00:58:37,539 --> 00:58:40,460
[SPEAKER_00] užeg geopolitičkog obzora,

1795
00:58:40,460 --> 00:58:42,139
[SPEAKER_00] ali isto tako i šireki.

1796
00:58:42,139 --> 00:58:43,639
[SPEAKER_00] To je vrlo važna stvar.

1797
00:58:43,639 --> 00:58:45,579
[SPEAKER_00] Šira slika.

1798
00:58:45,579 --> 00:58:47,480
[SPEAKER_00] Šira slika, bilo da je to Afganistan,

1799
00:58:47,480 --> 00:58:48,699
[SPEAKER_00] bilo da je to bliske istok.

1800
00:58:48,699 --> 00:58:50,300
[SPEAKER_00] I ono je vrlo, vrlo pametno,

1801
00:58:50,300 --> 00:58:51,780
[SPEAKER_00] pa je to vrlo osjetljiva politika.

1802
00:58:52,079 --> 00:58:54,119
[SPEAKER_00] Oni nemaju izlazak na more.

1803
00:58:54,119 --> 00:58:55,800
[SPEAKER_00] A s druge strane, nemoju zaboraviti,

1804
00:58:55,800 --> 00:58:57,960
[SPEAKER_00] ako idemo čak i po to jednoj genetskoj strani,

1805
00:58:57,960 --> 00:59:00,199
[SPEAKER_00] pa mi smo se tisuću godina s njima i ženili,

1806
00:59:00,199 --> 00:59:01,099
[SPEAKER_00] i miješali,

1807
00:59:01,099 --> 00:59:04,059
[SPEAKER_00] ko vodi možda imaju malo više i avarske te krvi,

1808
00:59:04,059 --> 00:59:05,780
[SPEAKER_00] i hunske i tako dalje,

1809
00:59:05,780 --> 00:59:08,460
[SPEAKER_00] ali pa, gledajte, ne znam što ljudi znaju.

1810
00:59:08,460 --> 00:59:11,119
[SPEAKER_00] Pa Budimpešta je do početka Prvog svjetskog rata,

1811
00:59:11,119 --> 00:59:12,639
[SPEAKER_00] ali imala 50% Njemaca.

1812
00:59:13,139 --> 00:59:14,420
[SPEAKER_00] nevim, 40% nešto manje.

1813
00:59:14,420 --> 00:59:15,860
[SPEAKER_00] Pragi isto tako.

1814
00:59:15,860 --> 00:59:17,219
[SPEAKER_00] Sad imaju nešto manje,

1815
00:59:17,219 --> 00:59:18,039
[SPEAKER_00] ali imaju i dobro,

1816
00:59:18,039 --> 00:59:19,539
[SPEAKER_00] imaju tamo i Njemaca i svašta.

1817
00:59:19,539 --> 00:59:21,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ja im u svajom slučaju želim dobro.

1818
00:59:21,519 --> 00:59:22,840
[SPEAKER_00] Logično i oni imaju.

1819
00:59:22,840 --> 00:59:25,159
[SPEAKER_00] Pazite, mi Hrvati stalno kukamo

1820
00:59:25,159 --> 00:59:27,260
[SPEAKER_00] kako smo mi zakinuti za Bosnu i Hercegovinu,

1821
00:59:27,260 --> 00:59:28,099
[SPEAKER_00] pa sve to stoje.

1822
00:59:28,099 --> 00:59:29,739
[SPEAKER_00] Pa jeste svjesni da je

1823
00:59:29,739 --> 00:59:32,079
[SPEAKER_00] da je sama Mađarska izgubila dvije treće,

1824
00:59:32,079 --> 00:59:35,840
[SPEAKER_00] najde, nije možda jednu polovinu svoja terena.

1825
00:59:35,840 --> 00:59:38,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ajde, nekako se nagodio sa Rumuncima,

1826
00:59:38,739 --> 00:59:41,039
[SPEAKER_00] isto tako je imao milijune,

1827
00:59:41,039 --> 00:59:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] milijuna Mađara živi i više u Rumunjskoj,

1828
00:59:44,000 --> 00:59:45,980
[SPEAKER_00] onda je u Slovačkoj isto tako.

1829
00:59:45,980 --> 00:59:48,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ipad vodi jednu pametnu politiku,

1830
00:59:48,420 --> 00:59:50,800
[SPEAKER_00] nije ono divljačko, nije ratoborna

1831
00:59:50,800 --> 00:59:53,539
[SPEAKER_00] i vjerujem da može biti jedna i jedna.

1832
00:59:53,539 --> 00:59:56,420
[SPEAKER_01] Jedno, ja mi su ga zvali Evropski Trump, jel?

1833
00:59:56,420 --> 00:59:58,539
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, i on ga je primio.

1834
00:59:58,539 --> 01:00:00,760
[SPEAKER_01] Trump je prošlo, kada je bio na mandatu, primili.

1835
01:00:00,760 --> 01:00:03,219
[SPEAKER_01] Jesu li, vidite onda velike sličnosti

1836
01:00:03,219 --> 01:00:05,179
[SPEAKER_01] i kojeg još Evropskog vođu vidite,

1837
01:00:05,179 --> 01:00:07,360
[SPEAKER_01] da tako kažem, u toj kutiji?

1838
01:00:07,360 --> 01:00:09,320
[SPEAKER_00] Pa vidim, evo, gospođu,

1839
01:00:09,320 --> 01:00:11,920
[SPEAKER_00] evo, fine gospodista,

1840
01:00:11,920 --> 01:00:12,679
[SPEAKER_00] šlank, koji vidi,

1841
01:00:12,679 --> 01:00:16,119
[SPEAKER_00] jepa, gospođa Alice Weidl,

1842
01:00:16,119 --> 01:00:17,579
[SPEAKER_00] Weidl, ona je šefica

1843
01:00:17,579 --> 01:00:19,559
[SPEAKER_00] šefica AFD-a.

1844
01:00:19,559 --> 01:00:22,019
[SPEAKER_00] AFD-a, fine gospodina.

1845
01:00:22,019 --> 01:00:23,980
[SPEAKER_01] Ali sad se prilično u Njemačkoj

1846
01:00:23,980 --> 01:00:26,780
[SPEAKER_01] dižu svi na zadnje noge, zbog rasta desnice,

1847
01:00:26,780 --> 01:00:28,440
[SPEAKER_01] opet se vraćamo na onu desnicu.

1848
01:00:28,440 --> 01:00:30,579
[SPEAKER_00] Da, gledajte, Mađarska i Francuska,

1849
01:00:30,579 --> 01:00:32,239
[SPEAKER_00] koliko god imaju jako stroge zakone,

1850
01:00:32,239 --> 01:00:33,320
[SPEAKER_00] antirivizionističke,

1851
01:00:33,320 --> 01:00:34,440
[SPEAKER_00] da po tome ne govorim,

1852
01:00:34,440 --> 01:00:35,440
[SPEAKER_00] znam iz prve ruka,

1853
01:00:35,440 --> 01:00:38,559
[SPEAKER_00] ali ipak vi neke stvari možete kazati,

1854
01:00:38,559 --> 01:00:40,599
[SPEAKER_00] možete jednu nacionalnu desnicu

1855
01:00:40,599 --> 01:00:43,039
[SPEAKER_00] bolje profilirati, što konačno vidimo u Hrvatskoj,

1856
01:00:43,039 --> 01:00:45,539
[SPEAKER_00] nego što je to moguće u jednoj Njemačkoj.

1857
01:00:45,820 --> 01:00:47,619
[SPEAKER_00] Upravo iz razloga, znamo koje,

1858
01:00:47,619 --> 01:00:49,739
[SPEAKER_00] taj jedna stigma drugog svjetskog rata,

1859
01:00:49,739 --> 01:00:51,579
[SPEAKER_00] svaki dan čujemo taj riječ,

1860
01:00:51,579 --> 01:00:54,900
[SPEAKER_00] Auschwitz, to ste čuli vjerojatno 240 miliona puta,

1861
01:00:54,900 --> 01:00:55,739
[SPEAKER_00] znam se to dnevno.

1862
01:00:55,739 --> 01:00:58,039
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, ali neki kažu da i Hrvati imaju stigmu,

1863
01:00:58,039 --> 01:01:00,119
[SPEAKER_01] Jasenovca, Usteša, Ante, Pavalića.

1864
01:01:00,119 --> 01:01:01,460
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo sreć, sreće,

1865
01:01:01,460 --> 01:01:02,219
[SPEAKER_00] ne, to je nesreće,

1866
01:01:02,219 --> 01:01:04,280
[SPEAKER_00] zgubili smo puno zgodnih, lijepih vojnika,

1867
01:01:04,280 --> 01:01:06,159
[SPEAKER_00] krasnih ljudi,

1868
01:01:06,159 --> 01:01:07,500
[SPEAKER_00] isto koliko desetak,

1869
01:01:07,500 --> 01:01:08,539
[SPEAKER_00] tisuća naših vojnika,

1870
01:01:08,539 --> 01:01:11,780
[SPEAKER_00] koliko je poznan čak i da ih dragovojati sa strani.

1871
01:01:11,780 --> 01:01:14,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ali mi smo imali rat.

1872
01:01:14,320 --> 01:01:16,599
[SPEAKER_00] To je na neki način bila naša katarza.

1873
01:01:16,599 --> 01:01:17,179
[SPEAKER_00] Kompenzacija.

1874
01:01:17,179 --> 01:01:18,400
[SPEAKER_00] Slačete, nismo tu sad,

1875
01:01:18,400 --> 01:01:20,039
[SPEAKER_00] da ne meni sad tu neko soli pamet

1876
01:01:20,039 --> 01:01:22,960
[SPEAKER_00] sa nekim žrtvoslovljem ekstraterestrijal,

1877
01:01:22,960 --> 01:01:25,059
[SPEAKER_00] da mi govori o nekim fašistima,

1878
01:01:25,059 --> 01:01:25,880
[SPEAKER_00] o Ustašama,

1879
01:01:25,980 --> 01:01:28,139
[SPEAKER_00] to mi danas smiješno zvuče, razumijete.

1880
01:01:28,139 --> 01:01:30,380
[SPEAKER_01] Profesore, gdje vidite Hrvatsku za pet godina?

1881
01:01:30,380 --> 01:01:32,139
[SPEAKER_01] I kako mi je vidite?

1882
01:01:32,139 --> 01:01:34,219
[SPEAKER_00] Ja vam mogu to s filozofske strane reći,

1883
01:01:34,219 --> 01:01:36,219
[SPEAKER_00] meni mi ja ne mogu tu sad tvrditi, znate.

1884
01:01:36,219 --> 01:01:38,139
[SPEAKER_01] Da, recite, koja je vaša teza.

1885
01:01:38,139 --> 01:01:39,519
[SPEAKER_00] Moja teza je, pa jeste,

1886
01:01:39,519 --> 01:01:40,679
[SPEAKER_00] povijest je uvijek otvorena.

1887
01:01:40,679 --> 01:01:43,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo, recimo, ovo je vrlo bitna situacija

1888
01:01:43,760 --> 01:01:45,800
[SPEAKER_00] što se sad zbiva u Izraelu,

1889
01:01:45,800 --> 01:01:47,360
[SPEAKER_00] jer sad dolazi jednog velikog,

1890
01:01:47,360 --> 01:01:50,119
[SPEAKER_00] mogu reći, povijestnog prijeloma sa ljevicom.

1891
01:01:50,119 --> 01:01:52,099
[SPEAKER_00] Jer sad se ljevica okreće protiv Izraela

1892
01:01:52,099 --> 01:01:53,860
[SPEAKER_00] indirektno protiv Židova u Americi,

1893
01:01:53,860 --> 01:01:55,500
[SPEAKER_00] što je vrlo, vrlo asimptomatično.

1894
01:01:55,500 --> 01:01:57,840
[SPEAKER_00] Druge strane, nemojte zaboraviti da

1895
01:01:57,840 --> 01:02:00,480
[SPEAKER_00] Izrael i židovski lobi u Americi,

1896
01:02:00,480 --> 01:02:01,699
[SPEAKER_00] koji su izuzetno jaki,

1897
01:02:01,699 --> 01:02:03,659
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek su paticali tu ljevicu

1898
01:02:03,659 --> 01:02:05,900
[SPEAKER_00] i te antife, antife koji su izuzetno jaki

1899
01:02:05,900 --> 01:02:07,360
[SPEAKER_00] u Americi, pogotovo na koleđima,

1900
01:02:07,360 --> 01:02:09,380
[SPEAKER_00] koji stvaraju javno mijenje.

1901
01:02:09,380 --> 01:02:11,019
[SPEAKER_00] I tu je jedna velika stvar,

1902
01:02:11,019 --> 01:02:13,159
[SPEAKER_00] tako da je sada općenita situacija

1903
01:02:13,159 --> 01:02:15,360
[SPEAKER_00] krajenja napeta, ne mislim toliko

1904
01:02:15,360 --> 01:02:16,840
[SPEAKER_00] i u vojnom smislu,

1905
01:02:16,840 --> 01:02:18,460
[SPEAKER_00] nego čisto u jednom

1906
01:02:18,460 --> 01:02:20,820
[SPEAKER_00] kulturno-hegemonijskom smislu.

1907
01:02:21,239 --> 01:02:24,480
[SPEAKER_00] Više nije to da ćete vi sad

1908
01:02:24,480 --> 01:02:25,820
[SPEAKER_00] doći na Američki koleđ

1909
01:02:25,820 --> 01:02:27,980
[SPEAKER_00] ili čak i u Francijski koleđ

1910
01:02:27,980 --> 01:02:30,800
[SPEAKER_00] i da ćete krasno uvijek

1911
01:02:30,800 --> 01:02:33,079
[SPEAKER_00] filosemitski i proizraelski

1912
01:02:33,079 --> 01:02:33,760
[SPEAKER_00] ići govoriti,

1913
01:02:33,760 --> 01:02:35,480
[SPEAKER_00] možete čak imati neugodnosti.

1914
01:02:35,480 --> 01:02:38,079
[SPEAKER_00] Odatle je rast tog famoznog antisemitizma,

1915
01:02:38,079 --> 01:02:39,599
[SPEAKER_00] a i u tu riječ bi mogli ići

1916
01:02:39,599 --> 01:02:41,260
[SPEAKER_00] molokiju, koja je na vrlo, vrlo

1917
01:02:41,260 --> 01:02:42,440
[SPEAKER_00] složene naravi, razumiju.

1918
01:02:42,440 --> 01:02:43,940
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, tu bi ja uzo,

1919
01:02:43,940 --> 01:02:46,320
[SPEAKER_00] što se tiče hrvatskog pitanja,

1920
01:02:46,320 --> 01:02:48,320
[SPEAKER_00] već u pet godina,

1921
01:02:48,320 --> 01:02:49,519
[SPEAKER_00] to mi je teško tu reći.

1922
01:02:50,380 --> 01:02:53,400
[SPEAKER_00] jednostavno, ono čak se ja bojim najviše,

1923
01:02:53,400 --> 01:02:56,940
[SPEAKER_00] tu mora vrlo brzo, vrlo hitno treba napraviti,

1924
01:02:56,940 --> 01:02:58,460
[SPEAKER_00] bilo da je to sola svoja,

1925
01:02:58,460 --> 01:03:00,840
[SPEAKER_00] bilo da su to naše vlade,

1926
01:03:00,840 --> 01:03:02,559
[SPEAKER_00] da se točno zna

1927
01:03:02,559 --> 01:03:04,280
[SPEAKER_00] ko će tu dolaziti od stranaca

1928
01:03:04,280 --> 01:03:06,460
[SPEAKER_00] i gledati da se napravi jedan vetting,

1929
01:03:06,460 --> 01:03:08,320
[SPEAKER_00] ali jedna trijaža,

1930
01:03:08,320 --> 01:03:10,619
[SPEAKER_00] da se zna da su ti ljudi, da su čisti,

1931
01:03:10,619 --> 01:03:13,059
