[SPEAKER_00] da tamo konobarim.

2144
01:07:39,179 --> 01:07:41,039
[SPEAKER_00] Čak jedna fina zagrećanka,

2145
01:07:41,039 --> 01:07:42,159
[SPEAKER_00] agramerka i šta ja znam,

2146
01:07:42,159 --> 01:07:44,179
[SPEAKER_00] školovana na filozofskom fakultetu,

2147
01:07:44,179 --> 01:07:45,360
[SPEAKER_00] bolje je tam ide raditi,

2148
01:07:45,360 --> 01:07:47,039
[SPEAKER_00] čistiti stojnjake i šta ja znam,

2149
01:07:47,039 --> 01:07:48,780
[SPEAKER_00] nego tu da se ide sramotiti

2150
01:07:48,780 --> 01:07:50,079
[SPEAKER_00] za tisuću eura

2151
01:07:50,079 --> 01:07:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] kod nekog našega primitivca,

2152
01:07:52,000 --> 01:07:52,719
[SPEAKER_00] da tako kažem.

2153
01:07:52,719 --> 01:07:55,179
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, odobravate ta isiljavanja,

2154
01:07:55,179 --> 01:07:56,360
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno, u stvari ne.

2155
01:07:56,360 --> 01:07:57,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ma ne, ne odobravam,

2156
01:07:57,539 --> 01:07:59,159
[SPEAKER_01] ali ne vidim jednostavno razlog.

2157
01:07:59,159 --> 01:08:00,039
[SPEAKER_01] Krivo sam postavila.

2158
01:08:00,039 --> 01:08:03,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ja tu ne vidim nikakve politike,

2159
01:08:03,320 --> 01:08:04,920
[SPEAKER_00] je ovo što možem odmah preložiti.

2160
01:08:04,920 --> 01:08:07,280
[SPEAKER_00] Treba hitno napraviti jednu

2161
01:08:07,280 --> 01:08:09,219
[SPEAKER_00] apsolutnu trijažu tih ljudi

2162
01:08:09,219 --> 01:08:10,059
[SPEAKER_00] ko tu dolaze.

2163
01:08:10,059 --> 01:08:12,659
[SPEAKER_00] I po mogućnosti nek dođu ljudi

2164
01:08:12,659 --> 01:08:14,780
[SPEAKER_00] koji pripadaju ne samo istom

2165
01:08:14,780 --> 01:08:15,760
[SPEAKER_00] kulturnom fondu,

2166
01:08:15,760 --> 01:08:17,819
[SPEAKER_00] nego također i genetskom fondu.

2167
01:08:17,819 --> 01:08:20,380
[SPEAKER_00] Evo imate dva i pol miliona

2168
01:08:20,380 --> 01:08:21,359
[SPEAKER_00] južnih afrikanaca,

2169
01:08:21,359 --> 01:08:22,960
[SPEAKER_00] joj morao sam tamo ići za ovome ljudi.

2170
01:08:22,960 --> 01:08:24,560
[SPEAKER_00] Oni tamo imaju svoja geta.

2171
01:08:24,560 --> 01:08:26,380
[SPEAKER_00] Imate negativnu diskriminaciju,

2172
01:08:26,380 --> 01:08:28,460
[SPEAKER_00] ali si vi svjesni što se zbiva u južnoj Africe?

2173
01:08:28,899 --> 01:08:30,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi ni ne znaju da je to zemlja

2174
01:08:30,880 --> 01:08:32,720
[SPEAKER_00] druga zemlja, bez odvira što su njihove sada

2175
01:08:32,720 --> 01:08:35,520
[SPEAKER_00] karnevale, što imaju protiv Izraelaca,

2176
01:08:35,520 --> 01:08:37,560
[SPEAKER_00] što tuže Izrael i tako dalje.

2177
01:08:37,560 --> 01:08:39,220
[SPEAKER_00] Ali bijelice su tamo,

2178
01:08:39,220 --> 01:08:40,680
[SPEAKER_00] to je dosta se postala

2179
01:08:40,680 --> 01:08:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] divljačna na meti, razumijete.

2180
01:08:44,000 --> 01:08:45,340
[SPEAKER_00] Njih se ugnjetava,

2181
01:08:45,340 --> 01:08:46,640
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo srednji stalež.

2182
01:08:46,640 --> 01:08:48,500
[SPEAKER_00] Imate broj nasilovanja.

2183
01:08:48,500 --> 01:08:51,380
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon Brazila to je druga zemlja na svijetu

2184
01:08:51,380 --> 01:08:52,560
[SPEAKER_00] po broju kriminala, razumijem.

2185
01:08:52,560 --> 01:08:54,359
[SPEAKER_00] Protiv bijelaca, da se nazujem.

2186
01:08:54,359 --> 01:08:56,439
[SPEAKER_00] Evo takvih 500 tisuća bijelaca

2187
01:08:56,439 --> 01:08:58,460
[SPEAKER_00] nek ovdje dođu da su pretižno buri.

2188
01:08:58,460 --> 01:08:59,779
[SPEAKER_01] Imao mi i naše Hrvate iz Južne Amerike.

2189
01:08:59,779 --> 01:09:00,760
[SPEAKER_00] Imate iz Južne Amerike.

2190
01:09:00,760 --> 01:09:02,539
[SPEAKER_00] Evo ga, pa čujte, iz prve ruke znam,

2191
01:09:02,539 --> 01:09:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] jer sam se, evo, fala kad ste mi postavili pitanje.

2192
01:09:05,000 --> 01:09:06,939
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam povratnik isto tako.

2193
01:09:06,939 --> 01:09:08,420
[SPEAKER_00] Šta ješ ti, gdje su ti?

2194
01:09:08,760 --> 01:09:10,439
[SPEAKER_00] Ali čujte, morate shvatiti ljude,

2195
01:09:10,439 --> 01:09:12,159
[SPEAKER_00] evo, s njima sam u svaki dan se čujem.

2196
01:09:12,159 --> 01:09:13,680
[SPEAKER_00] Iz Sidnija, iz Čikaga,

2197
01:09:13,680 --> 01:09:15,699
[SPEAKER_00] Melburna, iz Džilonga,

2198
01:09:15,699 --> 01:09:16,979
[SPEAKER_00] zvali su me par puta,

2199
01:09:16,979 --> 01:09:18,680
[SPEAKER_00] bio sam s gospodinom Glasnovićom dole,

2200
01:09:18,680 --> 01:09:20,140
[SPEAKER_00] a i sam sam išao dole.

2201
01:09:20,140 --> 01:09:21,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ali sad isto njih,

2202
01:09:21,539 --> 01:09:23,420
[SPEAKER_00] i vide da se tu mijenja,

2203
01:09:23,420 --> 01:09:24,899
[SPEAKER_00] Zagreb se isto mijenja,

2204
01:09:24,899 --> 01:09:28,600
[SPEAKER_00] da nije više demografska slika kao i prije.

2205
01:09:28,600 --> 01:09:30,739
[SPEAKER_00] I onda ljudi, malo i njima za mjerom,

2206
01:09:30,739 --> 01:09:31,220
[SPEAKER_00] razumijete?

2207
01:09:31,220 --> 01:09:32,939
[SPEAKER_00] Što oni isto, vala, očekuju,

2208
01:09:32,939 --> 01:09:34,819
[SPEAKER_00] tu sam ja i kritičan prema dijaspori,

2209
01:09:35,039 --> 01:09:36,779
[SPEAKER_00] vala, očekuju crveni tepi da će im dođe.

2210
01:09:36,779 --> 01:09:38,140
[SPEAKER_00] Nema, to isto ne volim.

2211
01:09:38,140 --> 01:09:40,140
[SPEAKER_00] Nema se šta sad uhrvatovati,

2212
01:09:40,140 --> 01:09:41,779
[SPEAKER_00] budi, bori se se kao i ja,

2213
01:09:41,779 --> 01:09:42,619
[SPEAKER_00] meni nije lagano,

2214
01:09:42,619 --> 01:09:44,460
[SPEAKER_00] 30 godina, 20 godina sam ovdje,

2215
01:09:44,460 --> 01:09:45,760
[SPEAKER_00] pa mi nije nimalo lagano.

2216
01:09:45,760 --> 01:09:47,859
[SPEAKER_00] I tu se potpuno slažnost ima,

2217
01:09:47,859 --> 01:09:50,180
[SPEAKER_00] međutim i tu čovjek mora malo biti izbirljiv.

2218
01:09:50,180 --> 01:09:52,039
[SPEAKER_00] A imamo kvalitetnih ljudi,

2219
01:09:52,039 --> 01:09:52,960
[SPEAKER_00] svugdje, pogotovo,

2220
01:09:52,960 --> 01:09:56,079
[SPEAKER_00] da sad skrećem digresiju.

2221
01:09:56,079 --> 01:09:57,800
[SPEAKER_00] Znate što mene pogodilo?

2222
01:09:57,800 --> 01:09:59,760
[SPEAKER_00] U Sidnji dođe, u Melbourne, u Džilong.

2223
01:10:01,319 --> 01:10:03,520
[SPEAKER_00] predivne, katoličke, hrvatske misije.

2224
01:10:03,520 --> 01:10:05,960
[SPEAKER_00] Pa mislim, znate kako to lepo izgleda?

2225
01:10:05,960 --> 01:10:08,039
[SPEAKER_00] To je super moderno, super klimatizirano,

2226
01:10:08,039 --> 01:10:09,600
[SPEAKER_00] tam su vrućine ogrome, znate.

2227
01:10:09,600 --> 01:10:11,600
[SPEAKER_00] Ja si mislim, bože moje,

2228
01:10:11,600 --> 01:10:14,020
[SPEAKER_00] to su teški milioni dolara tamo utučeni,

2229
01:10:14,020 --> 01:10:16,760
[SPEAKER_00] što bi stvorili su se te neke abstraktne,

2230
01:10:16,760 --> 01:10:19,699
[SPEAKER_00] ekstra planetarne hrvatske,

2231
01:10:19,699 --> 01:10:22,279
[SPEAKER_00] umjesto da se ta novac i taj trud

2232
01:10:22,279 --> 01:10:24,100
[SPEAKER_00] i svi ti ljudi da se to tu uložilo.

2233
01:10:24,100 --> 01:10:25,399
[SPEAKER_00] Mislite da se vrati doma?

2234
01:10:25,399 --> 01:10:27,500
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ne samo u novčanom smislu.

2235
01:10:27,500 --> 01:10:30,220
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, za to, ja ću biti toliko otvoren,

2236
01:10:30,220 --> 01:10:32,039
[SPEAKER_00] možda ću se nekom zamjeriti od kolega

2237
01:10:32,039 --> 01:10:34,239
[SPEAKER_00] iz državnog ureda za Hrvate

2238
01:10:34,239 --> 01:10:35,500
[SPEAKER_00] izvan Republike Hrvatske,

2239
01:10:35,500 --> 01:10:37,180
[SPEAKER_00] ali, Boga mi, ja ću reći otvor,

2240
01:10:37,180 --> 01:10:39,380
[SPEAKER_00] ja ne znam, ti svi silni uredi,

2241
01:10:39,380 --> 01:10:41,600
[SPEAKER_00] uključujući matica Hrvatske, svaka im čast.

2242
01:10:41,600 --> 01:10:43,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, dobro, sve je to lijepo,

2243
01:10:43,340 --> 01:10:45,239
[SPEAKER_00] ali nije Hrvatsko samo folklor,

2244
01:10:45,239 --> 01:10:47,739
[SPEAKER_00] to moramo shvatiti, tamburice i drmeži.

2245
01:10:47,739 --> 01:10:51,199
[SPEAKER_00] Hrvatsko to je jedna oblik sudbine, razumijete.

2246
01:10:54,100 --> 01:10:55,619
[SPEAKER_00] Hrvatovat samo sa bojama,

2247
01:10:55,619 --> 01:10:57,220
[SPEAKER_00] ili šta ja znam, svaka čast.

2248
01:10:57,220 --> 01:10:58,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ili za utakmicu.

2249
01:10:58,079 --> 01:10:59,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ili ići tamo u Konavlje,

2250
01:10:59,279 --> 01:11:00,880
[SPEAKER_00] sve su to krasne, njehove noštje,

2251
01:11:00,880 --> 01:11:03,439
[SPEAKER_00] sve ja to volim, ali nije to Hrvatsko.

2252
01:11:03,439 --> 01:11:05,119
[SPEAKER_00] I morate preći u jednostranje,

2253
01:11:05,119 --> 01:11:07,300
[SPEAKER_00] sve se to nas, nažalost, komercijalizira.

2254
01:11:07,300 --> 01:11:08,520
[SPEAKER_00] Čak i ovaj naš Lado,

2255
01:11:08,520 --> 01:11:11,180
[SPEAKER_00] kad vidim ženske sa onim ružom na šminkane

2256
01:11:11,180 --> 01:11:12,760
[SPEAKER_00] i sa onom maskorom luđočkom,

2257
01:11:12,760 --> 01:11:15,880
[SPEAKER_00] pa nisu naše bake tako izgledali, razumijete.

2258
01:11:15,880 --> 01:11:17,699
[SPEAKER_00] One možda tih detalja nisu svjesne,

2259
01:11:17,739 --> 01:11:18,920
[SPEAKER_00] jer to će vam stranati sreći.

2260
01:11:18,920 --> 01:11:21,579
[SPEAKER_01] Ali su danas prihvatljivije oku 21. stoljeća.

2261
01:11:21,579 --> 01:11:23,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ma, apsolutno, sve je to lijepo,

2262
01:11:23,699 --> 01:11:24,560
[SPEAKER_00] sve je to krasno,

2263
01:11:24,560 --> 01:11:26,460
[SPEAKER_00] sve je i ovo što je bilo u areni nedavno.

2264
01:11:26,460 --> 01:11:27,479
[SPEAKER_00] Sve je to lijepo,

2265
01:11:27,479 --> 01:11:30,619
[SPEAKER_00] ali uvijek je tu opasnost jednog komercijalizacija.

2266
01:11:30,619 --> 01:11:32,220
[SPEAKER_00] Uvijek tu ima jedan broj ljudi,

2267
01:11:32,220 --> 01:11:33,520
[SPEAKER_00] koje mi ne znamo u pozadini,

2268
01:11:33,520 --> 01:11:34,619
[SPEAKER_00] koji vuču konce

2269
01:11:34,619 --> 01:11:36,779
[SPEAKER_00] i koje zarađuju lijepe novce na tome, razumijete.

2270
01:11:37,020 --> 01:11:38,439
[SPEAKER_01] Što bi bi onda kao profesor,

2271
01:11:38,439 --> 01:11:41,680
[SPEAKER_01] na tri američka sveučilišta ste predavali, je li tako?

2272
01:11:41,680 --> 01:11:43,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ja, ja, da, na univerziju, da, u Kaliforniji, da.

2273
01:11:43,960 --> 01:11:46,319
[SPEAKER_01] A onda čovjek Hrvat

2274
01:11:46,319 --> 01:11:49,899
[SPEAKER_01] sa američkih sveučilišta,

2275
01:11:49,899 --> 01:11:52,420
[SPEAKER_01] što bi ste rekli danas prosječnom Hrvatu,

2276
01:11:52,420 --> 01:11:53,180
[SPEAKER_01] koji ima, ne znam,

2277
01:11:53,180 --> 01:11:56,760
[SPEAKER_01] 18, 20, 25, 30, 40 godina.

2278
01:11:56,760 --> 01:11:58,100
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, jednom mladom Hrvatu,

2279
01:11:58,100 --> 01:11:59,579
[SPEAKER_01] jednom Hrvatu srednjih godina.

2280
01:11:59,579 --> 01:12:02,020
[SPEAKER_01] Ovi stari, oni su već u depresiji.

2281
01:12:02,020 --> 01:12:04,300
[SPEAKER_00] A 18 godina, to mi je teško da reći.

2282
01:12:04,300 --> 01:12:06,399
[SPEAKER_00] Znate, to mi na neke privatne stvari podsjećate,

2283
01:12:06,460 --> 01:12:08,039
[SPEAKER_00] o kojoj ne bi rada baš išto govorit.

2284
01:12:08,039 --> 01:12:10,699
[SPEAKER_00] Znate, nije to samo ja koji odgajam djecu.

2285
01:12:10,699 --> 01:12:12,800
[SPEAKER_00] Djecu odgajaju i ti mobiteli,

2286
01:12:12,800 --> 01:12:14,920
[SPEAKER_00] odgajaju i ovi televizije.

2287
01:12:14,920 --> 01:12:16,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ja bi možda zabranio mobitele.

2288
01:12:16,460 --> 01:12:18,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ukazamo šta, sutra bi me objeseli.

2289
01:12:18,460 --> 01:12:19,939
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi im otjerali u zatvor.

2290
01:12:19,939 --> 01:12:22,720
[SPEAKER_00] I ja, nažalost, koristim taj mobitel više nego prije.

2291
01:12:22,720 --> 01:12:24,500
[SPEAKER_01] Dobar, kako da oni promišljaju tu Hrvatsku

2292
01:12:24,500 --> 01:12:27,020
[SPEAKER_01] na način kako vi smatrate da je potrebno?

2293
01:12:27,020 --> 01:12:29,640
[SPEAKER_00] Aha, nažalost, treba mi dati neke uzuse,

2294
01:12:29,640 --> 01:12:30,720
[SPEAKER_00] neke, neke modele.

2295
01:12:31,039 --> 01:12:32,539
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, ja iso tražim potporu.

2296
01:12:32,539 --> 01:12:33,300
[SPEAKER_00] A ko će?

2297
01:12:33,300 --> 01:12:36,340
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo, ima krasnih ljudi na Hrvatskim studijima,

2298
01:12:36,340 --> 01:12:38,020
[SPEAKER_00] ima ljudi na filosijskom fakultetu,

2299
01:12:38,020 --> 01:12:40,380
[SPEAKER_00] ali kad vi uđete u to jednu kolotečinu,

2300
01:12:40,380 --> 01:12:42,399
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek kad malo počnete će prkati,

2301
01:12:42,399 --> 01:12:44,079
[SPEAKER_00] gledati ljude malo fizijonomijama,

2302
01:12:44,079 --> 01:12:45,899
[SPEAKER_00] njegove, uvijek se sve svoje,

2303
01:12:45,899 --> 01:12:47,859
[SPEAKER_00] ili ću ja svoga sina tamo posliti,

2304
01:12:47,859 --> 01:12:49,779
[SPEAKER_00] ili ću pogurati nekog svoga,

2305
01:12:49,779 --> 01:12:51,340
[SPEAKER_00] ili ću dati možda na onako,

2306
01:12:51,340 --> 01:12:53,680
[SPEAKER_00] na brzo, potezno, nekom doktorati, sl.

2307
01:12:53,680 --> 01:12:56,460
[SPEAKER_00] Stvara se ta jedna koruptivna svijest,

2308
01:12:56,460 --> 01:12:59,159
[SPEAKER_00] što je naglašeno, ponavljam, upravo u liberalizmu.

2309
01:12:59,159 --> 01:13:00,760
[SPEAKER_00] Mi trebamo jednu pravu meritokraciju,

2310
01:13:00,760 --> 01:13:03,840
[SPEAKER_00] ili da nazovemo duhovnu aristokraciju.

2311
01:13:03,840 --> 01:13:06,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ne aristokraciju krvi, da budemo tvoren,

2312
01:13:06,199 --> 01:13:07,760
[SPEAKER_00] nego jednu duhovnu aristokraciju,

2313
01:13:07,760 --> 01:13:10,260
[SPEAKER_00] gdje će se prvo cijeniti duh,

2314
01:13:10,260 --> 01:13:12,220
[SPEAKER_00] a tek onda gdje će se Sunića,

2315
01:13:12,220 --> 01:13:14,439
[SPEAKER_00] kad dođe pitat prvo što si objavljio,

2316
01:13:14,439 --> 01:13:15,960
[SPEAKER_00] kako si knjigu napisao,

2317
01:13:15,960 --> 01:13:17,960
[SPEAKER_00] a ne da me pita kakva kola uvoziš,

2318
01:13:17,960 --> 01:13:18,560
[SPEAKER_00] ili tako daj.

2319
01:13:18,560 --> 01:13:19,520
[SPEAKER_00] Ma treba je to dobro.

2320
01:13:19,520 --> 01:13:20,340
[SPEAKER_01] Pa tko će tu povest?

2321
01:13:20,340 --> 01:13:21,920
[SPEAKER_01] Tko će tu povest?

2322
01:13:21,920 --> 01:13:24,220
[SPEAKER_00] Pa morate naći par ljude koje, kažem,

2323
01:13:24,220 --> 01:13:27,619
[SPEAKER_00] koje stavljaju interese svoje države,

2324
01:13:27,619 --> 01:13:29,380
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno interesene države,

2325
01:13:29,380 --> 01:13:31,539
[SPEAKER_00] zvoje zajednice iznad samog sebe.

2326
01:13:31,539 --> 01:13:33,020
[SPEAKER_01] Dajte mi, molim vas, imenujte nekog,

2327
01:13:33,020 --> 01:13:35,720
[SPEAKER_01] upalite svjetlo na kraju tunela.

2328
01:13:35,720 --> 01:13:38,220
[SPEAKER_00] A gledajte, evo mogu par ljudi naći možda,

2329
01:13:38,220 --> 01:13:39,899
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam, ali ja sam...

2330
01:13:39,899 --> 01:13:40,819
[SPEAKER_01] Po vašem mišljenju.

2331
01:13:40,819 --> 01:13:43,119
[SPEAKER_00] A kažete, opet, pa gledajte,

2332
01:13:43,119 --> 01:13:44,199
[SPEAKER_00] zasebno ljude.

2333
01:13:44,199 --> 01:13:46,739
[SPEAKER_00] Vi ćete naći neku izisnu kvalitetu.

2334
01:13:46,739 --> 01:13:48,979
[SPEAKER_00] Kod gospodje Krišta ćete možda naći

2335
01:13:48,979 --> 01:13:50,119
[SPEAKER_00] jednu izisnu kvalitetu.

2336
01:13:50,119 --> 01:13:52,500
[SPEAKER_00] Preli da ja zamijeram što je odmah izišla iz te stranke.

2337
01:13:52,500 --> 01:13:54,699
[SPEAKER_00] Možda je to neka druga stranka za...

2338
01:13:54,699 --> 01:13:55,899
[SPEAKER_00] Možda je to ona dobronamirna,

2339
01:13:55,899 --> 01:13:57,180
[SPEAKER_00] ona dobronamirna ima,

2340
01:13:57,180 --> 01:14:00,039
[SPEAKER_00] ali mora gledajte i kakve su posljedice toga, razumjeti.

2341
01:14:00,380 --> 01:14:02,739
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, možda ona bi neku funkciju mogla odigrati.

2342
01:14:02,739 --> 01:14:04,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ali druga stvar je,

2343
01:14:04,380 --> 01:14:06,239
[SPEAKER_00] vidite, te su toj, to su te posebne,

2344
01:14:06,239 --> 01:14:07,600
[SPEAKER_00] te naše i taštine i egoj.

2345
01:14:07,600 --> 01:14:09,699
[SPEAKER_00] Gospodina Glasnovića dobro znam,

2346
01:14:09,699 --> 01:14:11,579
[SPEAKER_00] uvijem možda na rijetkih ljudi,

2347
01:14:11,579 --> 01:14:13,760
[SPEAKER_00] koja možda ja najbolje poznam u cijelo Hrvatske,

2348
01:14:13,760 --> 01:14:16,159
[SPEAKER_00] znam njegovu familiju oši za imigranskih dana.

2349
01:14:16,159 --> 01:14:17,840
[SPEAKER_00] On je došao ovdje,

2350
01:14:17,840 --> 01:14:18,840
[SPEAKER_00] dosud da pogine,

2351
01:14:18,840 --> 01:14:21,079
[SPEAKER_00] da nije on gledao da li će ostati živ.

2352
01:14:21,079 --> 01:14:22,899
[SPEAKER_00] imao pristojnu penziju

2353
01:14:22,899 --> 01:14:24,720
[SPEAKER_00] i kao kanadski vojnik

2354
01:14:24,720 --> 01:14:25,960
[SPEAKER_00] i kao kanadski državni,

2355
01:14:25,960 --> 01:14:28,920
[SPEAKER_00] ali došao je ovdje tu da se zrstvoje

2356
01:14:28,920 --> 01:14:30,380
[SPEAKER_00] i vrlo skromno živi,

2357
01:14:30,380 --> 01:14:32,239
[SPEAKER_00] čak i ispasnički i tako dalje.

2358
01:14:32,239 --> 01:14:34,500
[SPEAKER_00] I on bi možda u nekoj funkciji,

2359
01:14:34,500 --> 01:14:36,779
[SPEAKER_00] ali međutim problem je u tome što bi on prihvatio,

2360
01:14:36,779 --> 01:14:37,319
[SPEAKER_00] razumijete?

2361
01:14:37,319 --> 01:14:40,699
[SPEAKER_00] Šta, ministar, čega, razumijete?

2362
01:14:40,699 --> 01:14:42,420
[SPEAKER_00] Teško je to reći.

2363
01:14:42,420 --> 01:14:44,239
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ja ne znam koga bi ima više.

2364
01:14:44,239 --> 01:14:46,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ima to još par ljudi koji bi ja mogo nabrojati.

2365
01:14:46,880 --> 01:14:48,800
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki od njih ima date svoje kvalitete

2366
01:14:48,800 --> 01:14:51,020
[SPEAKER_00] i neko može sad koji me gleda na televiziji,

2367
01:14:51,020 --> 01:14:51,979
[SPEAKER_00] možeš misliti,

2368
01:14:51,979 --> 01:14:54,239
[SPEAKER_00] a kaj Sunić sad tu u nama govori gluposti,

2369
01:14:54,239 --> 01:14:55,279
[SPEAKER_00] kaj bi ona pravil,

2370
01:14:55,279 --> 01:14:56,899
[SPEAKER_00] pa on to nema pojma što se zbiva.

2371
01:14:56,899 --> 01:14:58,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam.

2372
01:14:58,039 --> 01:14:59,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ja uvijek polazim od toga,

2373
01:14:59,460 --> 01:15:01,680
[SPEAKER_00] daj čovjeku, svakom daj njegovo.

2374
01:15:01,680 --> 01:15:03,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ono za što ste vi talentirani,

2375
01:15:03,840 --> 01:15:04,619
[SPEAKER_00] to radite.

2376
01:15:04,619 --> 01:15:06,439
[SPEAKER_00] Nemojte me u nešto tjerati,

2377
01:15:06,439 --> 01:15:07,640
[SPEAKER_00] to djeci kazali.

2378
01:15:07,640 --> 01:15:10,119
[SPEAKER_00] Nemojte tjerati nekog da ide u neke,

2379
01:15:10,119 --> 01:15:12,819
[SPEAKER_00] kako se to zove učilišta,

2380
01:15:12,819 --> 01:15:14,760
[SPEAKER_00] verne ili te razne škole,

2381
01:15:14,760 --> 01:15:17,260
[SPEAKER_00] neću vrijeđati, nisam to upoznan.

2382
01:15:17,260 --> 01:15:19,359
[SPEAKER_00] Ako čovjeku srce diše,

2383
01:15:19,359 --> 01:15:21,319
[SPEAKER_00] da piše dobri pjesmi,

2384
01:15:21,319 --> 01:15:22,659
[SPEAKER_00] da svira klavir,

2385
01:15:22,659 --> 01:15:24,600
[SPEAKER_00] nemoj ga tjerati da bude biznismen.

2386
01:15:24,600 --> 01:15:26,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ako je čovjek dobar matematičar,

2387
01:15:26,579 --> 01:15:28,300
[SPEAKER_00] nemoj ga onda tjerati da ide

2388
01:15:28,300 --> 01:15:29,859
[SPEAKER_00] književno studirati

2389
01:15:29,859 --> 01:15:31,180
[SPEAKER_00] ili da ide jezike studirati,

2390
01:15:31,180 --> 01:15:32,579
[SPEAKER_00] kao što sam ja išao studirati.

2391
01:15:32,579 --> 01:15:34,239
[SPEAKER_00] Ako čovjeku ide dobro,

2392
01:15:34,239 --> 01:15:36,619
[SPEAKER_00] ako znam metaforički razmišljati,

2393
01:15:36,619 --> 01:15:38,939
[SPEAKER_00] daj ga pošalji onda na dobre studije,

2394
01:15:38,939 --> 01:15:40,159
[SPEAKER_00] čak i van ako treba,

2395
01:15:40,159 --> 01:15:41,500
[SPEAKER_00] i na Oxfordi, na Cambridgei,

2396
01:15:41,500 --> 01:15:43,300
[SPEAKER_00] ili na Pennsylvania University,

2397
01:15:43,300 --> 01:15:44,560
[SPEAKER_00] su dobri univerziteti,

2398
01:15:44,560 --> 01:15:45,579
[SPEAKER_00] ima načina.

2399
01:15:45,579 --> 01:15:46,779
[SPEAKER_00] Pa onda ga to,

2400
01:15:46,779 --> 01:15:48,260
[SPEAKER_00] nek se tamo specializira,

2401
01:15:48,260 --> 01:15:50,100
[SPEAKER_00] ali nipa što da nešto radi,

2402
01:15:50,100 --> 01:15:51,600
[SPEAKER_00] što je suprotno njegovom duhu,

2403
01:15:51,600 --> 01:15:52,199
[SPEAKER_00] razumijete?

2404
01:15:52,199 --> 01:15:53,140
[SPEAKER_01] Njegovom DNK.

2405
01:15:53,140 --> 01:15:55,180
[SPEAKER_00] Eto, njegovom DNK.

2406
01:15:55,180 --> 01:15:57,420
[SPEAKER_00] Nemojte me na to tjerati.

2407
01:15:57,420 --> 01:15:59,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ja isto ko mali dečkog,

2408
01:15:59,199 --> 01:16:00,720
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam završio gimnaziju,

2409
01:16:00,720 --> 01:16:02,520
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje tu izgubio sam godinu,

2410
01:16:02,520 --> 01:16:04,520
[SPEAKER_00] 71. radi mog Čače,

2411
01:16:04,520 --> 01:16:05,539
[SPEAKER_00] jer on je imao problema,

2412
01:16:05,539 --> 01:16:07,619
[SPEAKER_00] šta ja znam,

2413
01:16:07,619 --> 01:16:09,479
[SPEAKER_00] zate kako je 71. godine bila,

2414
01:16:09,479 --> 01:16:10,859
[SPEAKER_00] ali imao sam,

2415
01:16:10,859 --> 01:16:11,819
[SPEAKER_00] volio sam čitati.

2416
01:16:11,819 --> 01:16:13,260
[SPEAKER_00] Neko voli čitati.

2417
01:16:13,260 --> 01:16:14,619
[SPEAKER_00] I volio sam čitati,

2418
01:16:14,619 --> 01:16:15,560
[SPEAKER_00] i nekako sam se,

2419
01:16:15,560 --> 01:16:17,319
[SPEAKER_00] imao sam sreću nakon toga.

2420
01:16:17,319 --> 01:16:19,279
[SPEAKER_01] I među ostalim je ovo rezultat

2421
01:16:19,279 --> 01:16:21,479
[SPEAKER_01] vaše ljubavi prema čitanju,

2422
01:16:21,479 --> 01:16:23,159
[SPEAKER_01] da, niz objavljenih knjiga.

2423
01:16:23,159 --> 01:16:23,739
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

2424
01:16:23,739 --> 01:16:25,060
[SPEAKER_00] I nisam neke stvari,

2425
01:16:25,060 --> 01:16:25,979
[SPEAKER_00] treba me sad pitati

2426
01:16:25,979 --> 01:16:27,840
[SPEAKER_00] da imam voziti kran,

2427
01:16:27,840 --> 01:16:28,739
[SPEAKER_00] ili da se njegovom,

2428
01:16:28,739 --> 01:16:30,300
[SPEAKER_00] možda bi mogo napraviti,

2429
01:16:30,300 --> 01:16:30,960
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne bi dobro.

2430
01:16:31,279 --> 01:16:32,460
[SPEAKER_01] Zapravo, to je poruka.

2431
01:16:32,460 --> 01:16:34,060
[SPEAKER_01] Svakome njegovo.

2432
01:16:34,060 --> 01:16:35,020
[SPEAKER_00] Svakome njegovo.

2433
01:16:35,020 --> 01:16:36,279
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, dobar sam u PR,

2434
01:16:36,279 --> 01:16:37,840
[SPEAKER_00] tu sam kad sam bio diplomat,

2435
01:16:37,840 --> 01:16:38,779
[SPEAKER_00] to sam dobar PR,

2436
01:16:38,779 --> 01:16:40,560
[SPEAKER_00] i ljud sam na našo te isto

2437
01:16:40,560 --> 01:16:41,520
[SPEAKER_00] kvazi diplomate,

2438
01:16:41,520 --> 01:16:42,600
[SPEAKER_00] veliku većinu njih,

2439
01:16:42,600 --> 01:16:43,420
[SPEAKER_00] čak i dan danas,

2440
01:16:43,420 --> 01:16:44,319
[SPEAKER_00] zamjeram,

2441
01:16:44,319 --> 01:16:46,100
[SPEAKER_00] ajde, ako mogu mi dozvoljavati,

2442
01:16:46,100 --> 01:16:46,920
[SPEAKER_00] jer ne volim ono,

2443
01:16:46,920 --> 01:16:47,779
[SPEAKER_00] ad homines,

2444
01:16:47,779 --> 01:16:48,680
[SPEAKER_00] sad upljuvat ljude,

2445
01:16:48,680 --> 01:16:50,300
[SPEAKER_00] ali cijela ta postavka

2446
01:16:50,300 --> 01:16:52,279
[SPEAKER_00] u našoj diplomaciji je loša,

2447
01:16:52,279 --> 01:16:53,819
[SPEAKER_00] dosta provincijski dijeluje.

2448
01:16:53,819 --> 01:16:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne možete vi obeć slati ljude

2449
01:16:56,000 --> 01:16:57,399
[SPEAKER_00] koji ne znaju njemački je.

2450
01:16:57,479 --> 01:16:59,300
[SPEAKER_00] To moraju savršeno poznavat njemački

2451
01:16:59,300 --> 01:17:01,300
[SPEAKER_00] ili ne možete na engleskom

2452
01:17:01,300 --> 01:17:03,460
[SPEAKER_00] komunicirati sa jednim

2453
01:17:03,460 --> 01:17:04,619
[SPEAKER_00] francusom, razumete.

2454
01:17:04,619 --> 01:17:05,420
[SPEAKER_00] To tako ne ide.

2455
01:17:05,420 --> 01:17:06,460
[SPEAKER_00] On vam to neće kazati,

2456
01:17:06,460 --> 01:17:07,619
[SPEAKER_00] ali to su nijanse sve.

2457
01:17:08,260 --> 01:17:09,119
[SPEAKER_00] tu je jedna elita,

2458
01:17:09,119 --> 01:17:10,779
[SPEAKER_00] ja nažalost nisam imao to sreće,

2459
01:17:10,779 --> 01:17:11,899
[SPEAKER_00] još sam nažalost došao

2460
01:17:11,899 --> 01:17:13,479
[SPEAKER_00] u to jedno posljednje gnjezdo,

2461
01:17:13,479 --> 01:17:14,899
[SPEAKER_00] ali nisam se dao.

2462
01:17:14,899 --> 01:17:16,920
[SPEAKER_00] A borim se, čujte,

2463
01:17:16,920 --> 01:17:18,460
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek volim će cijat nića,

2464
01:17:18,460 --> 01:17:19,479
[SPEAKER_00] a ja sam nićarac.

2465
01:17:19,479 --> 01:17:22,520
[SPEAKER_00] Slobodan čovjek i borac.

2466
01:17:22,520 --> 01:17:24,420
[SPEAKER_01] Da, i ostati će takav.

2467
01:17:24,420 --> 01:17:26,300
[SPEAKER_01] A i tu i tamo u depresiji.

2468
01:17:26,300 --> 01:17:28,079
[SPEAKER_00] A da, morate se stalno boriti.

2469
01:17:28,079 --> 01:17:29,039
[SPEAKER_00] Život je borba.

2470
01:17:29,039 --> 01:17:31,539
[SPEAKER_01] Profesore, bilo je super,

2471
01:17:31,539 --> 01:17:32,180
[SPEAKER_01] barem medi,

2472
01:17:32,180 --> 01:17:34,359
[SPEAKER_01] nadam se i našim gledateljima.

2473
01:17:34,359 --> 01:17:37,279
[SPEAKER_01] I reći ćemo samo ovo prva epizoda

2474
01:17:37,279 --> 01:17:38,739
[SPEAKER_01] profesora Tomislava Sunića

2475
01:17:38,739 --> 01:17:39,659
[SPEAKER_01] u podcastu Mrežnica,

2476
01:17:39,659 --> 01:17:41,579
[SPEAKER_01] jer doista puno tema imamo

2477
01:17:41,579 --> 01:17:42,560
[SPEAKER_01] za obraditi.

2478
01:17:42,560 --> 01:17:43,220
[SPEAKER_01] Je li tako?

2479
01:17:43,220 --> 01:17:43,899
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala lijepa.

2480
01:17:43,899 --> 01:17:45,060
[SPEAKER_00] Volim Rijeku Mrežnicu

2481
01:17:45,060 --> 01:17:45,880
[SPEAKER_00] i to ću vas pitati

2482
01:17:45,880 --> 01:17:47,539
[SPEAKER_00] jer sam se tamo okupao prošle godine.

2483
01:17:47,539 --> 01:17:49,220
[SPEAKER_00] To mi je ono najljepši trenutak

2484
01:17:49,220 --> 01:17:49,899
[SPEAKER_00] je bio u životu.

2485
01:17:49,899 --> 01:17:50,420
[SPEAKER_01] Eto, bravo.

2486
01:17:50,420 --> 01:17:51,359
[SPEAKER_01] Podcast Mrežnica,

2487
01:17:51,359 --> 01:17:52,520
[SPEAKER_01] vi volite Rijeku Mrežnicu.

2488
01:17:52,520 --> 01:17:53,119
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ono,

2489
01:17:53,119 --> 01:17:54,819
[SPEAKER_01] riješili smo sav problem,

2490
01:17:54,819 --> 01:17:56,640
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno dogovorili smo koaliciju.

2491
01:17:56,640 --> 01:17:57,479
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala lijepa.

2492
01:17:57,479 --> 01:17:57,920
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala vam.

2493
01:17:57,920 --> 01:18:00,199
[SPEAKER_01] Bio je ovo još jedan podcast Mrežnica.

2494
01:18:00,199 --> 01:18:01,180
[SPEAKER_01] Naš gost bio je

2495
01:18:07,279 --> 01:18:10,699
[UNKNOWN] Hvala što pratite kanal.

